				"name":"AI Video Generator & Image Generator by Photo AI",
				"description":"Generate photorealistic images and videos of people with AI. Take stunning photos of people with the first AI Photographer! Generate photo and video content for your social media with AI. Save time and money and do an AI photo shoot from your laptop or phone instead of hiring an expensive photographer. Take photos featuring yourself as an AI model. Every AI model you create gets FREE photos. Now with super fast training meaning you get your first photos in less than a minute!\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\u270f\ufe0f Upload your selfies \u2192 Create an AI model of yourself\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\ud83d\udc78 ...or create a 100% AI influencer to monetize\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\ud83d\udcf8 Then take AI photos with your AI model in any pose, place or action\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\ud83c\udfa5 And create AI Mocap videos starring your AI model as the main character\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\u2764\ufe0f Run 100s of photo packs like Clean Girl Aesthetic or Instagram\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\ud83c\udf81 Create product videos and try on clothes with your AI model\n\t\t",
				"sku":"",
				"category":"Photo Shoots",
				"mainEntityOfPage":{
					"@id":"https://photoai.com/#webpage"
				},
				"aggregateRating":{
					"@type":"AggregateRating",
					"ratingValue":"4.80",
					"bestRating":"5",
					"ratingCount":"2183",
					"reviewCount":"2183"
				},
				"review":[
															{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-1",
						"description":"I have been searching for an AI image generator that could generate very accurate pictures with realistic likeness of faces for which it is trained. PhotoAI is stunningly accurate in its ability to generate uncanny likeness of my chosen models in scenarios specified. I have tried 5 different AI image generators and built LoRAs with SDXL base and could never quite get satisfactory results. I was able to do it relatively easily with PhotoAI.",
						"datePublished":"2024-08-16 09:33:41",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"5",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Demersonian"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-2",
						"description":"Not a perfect AI tool, but still fairly amazing and getting better with time. As long as you upload good quality and type of pictures for training your model, does a reasonably good job with likeness. Does a really nice job of creating or matching clothing, creating custom settings. Processing time is now typically 12-20 seconds per image.",
						"datePublished":"2024-10-26 14:22:08",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"4",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Pete"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-3",
						"description":"Photo AI is just fantastic! I take amazing photos of my wife, family, friends and also incredible selfies. As a Photographer I found it very useful for testing ideas before creating a real photoshoot. It is in constant evolution with very frequent updates. I strongly recommend!",
						"datePublished":"2023-08-14 11:45:33",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"5",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Everaldo Coelho"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-4",
						"description":"I really enjoy using Photo AI. I do have to be very specific with my prompts, and there was definitely a learning curve. However, now I am getting some great results. I started here because I was looking for quality videos, and I found them!",
						"datePublished":"2025-07-15 10:18:55",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"4",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Vanessa Moyers"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-5",
						"description":"Overall using Photo AI has been a great experience, especially compared with other AI image generators. I was recommended to the site and subscribed for a month to check it out and I was very impressed. It helps to upload more than 20 images of yourself at the start to train the AI. After getting the monthly subscription I will definitely be getting the premium subscription next.",
						"datePublished":"2024-01-13 16:27:19",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"5",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Morpheus"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-6",
						"description":"I really enjoy this app - it is really the only one that I know of that can make realistic photos. It does a good job. It is only as good as the prompts you set up for it and the photos it is based on. If you are at least decent at writing an AI prompt and feed it good photos, the results are great.",
						"datePublished":"2023-12-21 08:44:12",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"5",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Michael P."
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-7",
						"description":"Good input = good output. Very fun! Took me some effort to get the models to feel accurate but once I got the right input it was amazing. Company was very responsive to my questions.",
						"datePublished":"2023-08-20 13:31:23",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"5",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Jordan Donaldson"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-8",
						"description":"Pretty good service. Models look very similar to photos. But I have had issues creating models on mobile when using large dataset. Text to video does not always work the best. Would also like to see ability to purchase tokens separately.",
						"datePublished":"2025-01-16 09:55:38",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"4",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Andrew Do"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-9",
						"description":"I resized 7 photos for free with AI, it worked wonderfully. Six photos were of people and one photo was food on a table. The tool correctly expanded each photo by about 70 pixels on each side. Very happy to finally find a tool that does something useful for free.",
						"datePublished":"2024-08-27 15:08:44",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"5",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Fred Fuchs"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-10",
						"description":"After exploring lots of AI platforms, Photo AI and Midjourney stand out. While Midjourney presents challenges in creating images with yourself in it, Photo AI excels at it. With enhancements in the clothes try on feature, it has the potential to be useful for many Shopify outlets. Great execution!",
						"datePublished":"2023-08-20 10:22:17",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"5",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Jason"
						}
					}
										,					{
						"@type":"Review",
						"@id":"https://photoai.com/#review-default-11",
						"description":"My experience was pretty good. I paid the subscription fee to speed up shopping for wedding attire, trying on different suits digitally instead of driving around to various tailors. They are not completely perfect, but they look eerily accurate considering my input photos. It has been a great help in coordinating colors for my suit.",
						"datePublished":"2023-10-30 11:15:42",
						"reviewRating":{
							"@type":"Rating",
							"ratingValue":"4",
							"bestRating":"5",
							"worstRating":"1"
						},
						"author":{
							"@type":"Person",
							"name":"Levi Kane"
						}
					}
									],
