								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want to merge two photos into a single AI-generated image? <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq10\">Photo AI<\/a> makes it effortless \u2014 no editing or Photoshop skills needed:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6849ee529a4b8bb66044d1c2\/019760dc-0232-73f3-a299-8343d2255fd1\/b64u-Y29tYmluZWZhcS53ZWJw.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"combinefaq.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6849ee529a4b8bb66044d1c2\/019760dc-0232-73f3-a299-8343d2255fd1\/b64u-Y29tYmluZWZhcS53ZWJw.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=32b226bb4c7ff03af36d7ebb0d29fa8e8bac7b6644729f07499077628399cc3c\"><h2 id=\"m6tcs32c02w\" data-toc-id=\"m6tcs32c02w\">1. Press [ Select ] in the top right of your Photo AI gallery<\/h2><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6849ee529a4b8bb66044d1c2\/019760d6-4048-7d44-8a91-45ce455b0122\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTEgYXQgMjIuMTAuMDIucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-11 at 22.10.02.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6849ee529a4b8bb66044d1c2\/019760d6-4048-7d44-8a91-45ce455b0122\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTEgYXQgMjIuMTAuMDIucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=a77f41ff366085bdfbdf0dde6cb9c72b1001f493c7c19de7cdb552b05e81782b\"><h2 id=\"r1epf5044zc\" data-toc-id=\"r1epf5044zc\">2. Select two photos you want to combine<\/h2><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6849ee529a4b8bb66044d1c2\/019760d6-750f-74a3-b4d5-e9138586dc39\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTEgYXQgMjIuMTAuNDMucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-11 at 22.10.43.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6849ee529a4b8bb66044d1c2\/019760d6-750f-74a3-b4d5-e9138586dc39\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTEgYXQgMjIuMTAuNDMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=d6663c4a7af8f7af19083aa9168cb716b4eaf263a7b2a0f837e58b2ed5022c6d\"><h2 id=\"qqkzs70p757\" data-toc-id=\"qqkzs70p757\">3. Press [ Combine photos ] at the bottom of the screen.<\/h2><p>That\u2019s it! In about 10\u201320 seconds, your photos will be fused into a single AI-generated image that blends elements of both \u2014 keeping the identity of the people and style intact. And there it is:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6849ee529a4b8bb66044d1c2\/019760d6-c4dd-7dd9-b7ea-525da4435a42\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTEgYXQgMjIuMTEuMTAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-11 at 22.11.10.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6849ee529a4b8bb66044d1c2\/019760d6-c4dd-7dd9-b7ea-525da4435a42\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTEgYXQgMjIuMTEuMTAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=dd751199893d30655e0cf797d75c97ee571c2ae9cb78280a5c5019672bf10597\"><p>If you press [ Make video ] after you can even turn your combined photo into a real-life video:<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NjBlZS1mNDM4LTczZjItOTNiOC01MzRlNjEzYTkwZGEiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDllZTUyOWE0YjhiYjY2MDQ0ZDFjMiIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTY3Nzk2M30.2_8ucz0Nw2n9P8PGzzcsTeDv1wnOBbSazL7uZQfhuD4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NjBlZS1mNDM4LTczZjItOTNiOC01MzRlNjEzYTkwZGEiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ5ZWU1MjlhNGI4YmI2NjA0NGQxYzIiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.xiMd3W2Qjm-ktNXmQ0TP3J_453rO4B76nFqq24eC9R0\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"wmsqxy17ty5\" data-toc-id=\"wmsqxy17ty5\">What is it good for?<\/h2><p>This feature is perfect for:<\/p><p>\u2022 Creating group shots from separate images<\/p><p>\u2022 Generating \u201cwhat if\u201d scenes<\/p><p>\u2022 Merging styles or outfits<\/p><p>Give it a try on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq10\">Photo AI<\/a> and create something new from what you already have!<\/p><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/photo-ai-free">
							Photo AI's Free Photos - What You Get & How To Start						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Photo AI's Free Photos - What You Get & How To Start",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Every Pro, Max and Ultra subscription to Photo AI now gives you a big set of free photos for every new model you create! That means thousands of free photos for Ultra plan subscribers.<\/p><p>If you become a yearly subscriber, you get 6+ months free.<\/p><p>For the plans itself you can check the <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/#pricing\">pricing<\/a> here.<\/p><p>Photo AI subscriptions are paid though for a reason:<\/p><p>Remember all those amazing free apps and services you used that eventually shut down, got acquired, or disappeared overnight? That\u2019s because free services usually can\u2019t sustain themselves financially. Here\u2019s why:<\/p><p>Running a service like Photo AI costs money: servers, development, maintenance, and ongoing improvements. If an app is free, it either burns through the founder\u2019s savings, relies on venture capital, or makes money by selling your data. None of these options guarantee the app\u2019s long-term survival.<\/p><p>Take the typical \u201cfree app\u201d story: <br>\u2022 A developer builds a cool, free product. <br>\u2022 It gains popularity but can\u2019t generate revenue, so it gets sold to a bigger company. <br>\u2022 The new owner shuts it down or ruins it, leaving users without the service they loved.<\/p><p>We don\u2019t want that to happen with Photo AI.<\/p><p>Instead, by charging for the service, we can stay independent, cover our costs, and continue improving the app for our users. We\u2019re not a venture-funded startup forced to grow at all costs or sell out to the highest bidder. We\u2019re a 100% owner independent platform focused on delivering real value to our users without compromising on quality or ethics.<\/p><p>If you like what we do, support Photo AI by becoming a paid user. It ensures we can keep building the features you love while staying here for the long term.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/what-ai-model-do-you-use">
							What AI model do you use?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "What AI model do you use?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">Photo AI uses its own generation pipeline which is trained for high photorealism. The main generation pipeline we use now is our own proprietary [ \u26a1\ufe0f Hyper Realism]. We use many other models to perform other functions like post-processing, upscaling, taking videos, adding audio to videos, adding voice to videos etc.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">We keep working on improving our pipeline using reinforcement learning from human feedback (RLHF) by users like you which constantly improves our models.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">All of this to get you better more photorealistic photos and videos!<\/span><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
