										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/how-much-does-it-cost-to-generate-on-photo-ai-how-do-credits-work">
							How much does it cost to generate on Photo AI? How do credits work?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How much does it cost to generate on Photo AI? How do credits work?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>The credit system on Photo AI is very simple. Every type of membership receives a certain amount of credits every month. If you have an annual subscription, your credits are also renewed every month.<\/p><table style=\"minWidth: 50px\"><colgroup><col><col><\/colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Feature<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p><strong>Credits per generation<\/strong><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Photo with Hyper Realism<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>1<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Photo with Nano Banana Pro<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>5<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Import photo into gallery<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>1<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Video (with sound)<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>30<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Talking video per character<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>3 per 100 characters<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Make 3d model<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>20<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Upscale<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>5<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Mocap video<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>10<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Zoom out photo<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>5<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Relight<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>5<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Add grain<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>1<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Combine photos<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>1<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>Upscale<\/p><\/td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p>5<\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><p>You can see your current credits in the top right of Photo AI:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6970e9608b3a93a25ab3172e\/019be111-335d-7ab5-b172-9c8f1ef75a0b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjEgYXQgMTQuNTkuMDMucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2026-01-21 at 14.59.03.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6970e9608b3a93a25ab3172e\/019be111-335d-7ab5-b172-9c8f1ef75a0b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjEgYXQgMTQuNTkuMDMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=6c9bd42291ee517901c4d2b975c1f28f23497c4c524a45df3e123d1f234c3009\"><p>The large number shows your subscriptions credits, and the small number are your \u201cextra credits\u201d. Unlike regular credits that expire every month, extra credits only expire after 2 years and you can top them up at any time in case you need to generate more content. To top up your credits tap \u201cBuy more credits\u201d.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6970e9608b3a93a25ab3172e\/019be112-04f9-7832-b475-f375274c518a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjEgYXQgMTUuMDAuMDIucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2026-01-21 at 15.00.02.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6970e9608b3a93a25ab3172e\/019be112-04f9-7832-b475-f375274c518a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjEgYXQgMTUuMDAuMDIucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=f102eb43cf86ac7ab9dd6d25c62aedf913b9ed99d68cc15aeca070d44c21b504\"><p>On the credits page you can choose how many credits to add, the more you buy the higher the discount you get:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6970e9608b3a93a25ab3172e\/019be113-0dce-7c01-8b18-30b78bd2fcd5\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjEgYXQgMTUuMDAuNDUucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2026-01-21 at 15.00.45.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6970e9608b3a93a25ab3172e\/019be113-0dce-7c01-8b18-30b78bd2fcd5\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjEgYXQgMTUuMDAuNDUucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=9fcc03f83a93a3005e0532840f60188cb53e686f65b0023a17e81bb54634c2ec\"><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/who-created-photo-ai-meet-pieter-levels-the-founder">
							Who created Photo AI? Meet Pieter Levels, the Founder						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Who created Photo AI? Meet Pieter Levels, the Founder",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">This service was built by me, <\/span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/levelsio\">Pieter Levels (@levelsio)<\/a><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">, a Dutch indie entrepreneur known for other projects like <\/span><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/nomads.com\">Nomad<\/a><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/nomads.com\">s.com<\/a><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">, <\/span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/remoteok.com\/\">Remote OK<\/a><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">, and <\/span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/interiorai.com\/\">Interior AI<\/a><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">It is a 100%-owned independent business without investors.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">I run it all by myself, with the help of thousands of AI robots \u263a\ufe0f<\/span><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
