								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want to get free credits on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq11\">Photo AI<\/a>? <\/p><p>Share Photo AI with friends, and you <em>both<\/em> earn credits. It\u2019s simple and fast.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684b13d2461fd1b42841f83c\/0197654a-3455-7fca-ad22-4506b08fc7f7\/b64u-MDE5NzY1NGEtMzNmNC03MmE0LThmMDUtM2VhNmIyMDE3NTRi.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684b13d2461fd1b42841f83c\/0197654a-3455-7fca-ad22-4506b08fc7f7\/b64u-MDE5NzY1NGEtMzNmNC03MmE0LThmMDUtM2VhNmIyMDE3NTRi.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=fa4d24ada33a8506c95b6d26559fb8cbd40eede6c5886a69b9a9016da7fa077a\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197654a-33f4-72a4-8f05-3ea6b201754b\"><h2 id=\"w60pm8byxri\" data-toc-id=\"w60pm8byxri\"><strong>How It Works<\/strong><\/h2><ol><li><p class=\"p1\"><strong>Click the Photo AI logo<\/strong> in the top left corner<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">In the dropdown, select <strong>[ Referral program ]<\/strong><\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">You\u2019ll get your personal invite link, like:<\/p><p class=\"p2\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?via=r123\">https:\/\/photoai.com\/?via=r123<\/a><\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Share it anywhere\u2014chat, email, socials<\/p><\/li><\/ol><h2 id=\"ii1wrfx4q8i\" data-toc-id=\"ii1wrfx4q8i\"><strong>The Rewards<\/strong><\/h2><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">If your friend signs up using your link:<\/p><p class=\"p2\"><\/p><ul><li><p class=\"p1\"><strong>You get 1,000 credits<\/strong><\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><strong>They get 1,000 credits<\/strong><\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><strong>Starter plan?<\/strong> You both get <strong>100 credits<\/strong> instead<\/p><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><h2 id=\"5z4zx54r0qc\" data-toc-id=\"5z4zx54r0qc\"><strong>No limits<\/strong><\/h2><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">Invite as many people as you want<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Credits stack with each signup<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h2 id=\"qrmo4028c4m\" data-toc-id=\"qrmo4028c4m\"><strong>Tips<\/strong><\/h2><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">Add your referral link to your bio or social profiles<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Post example AI edits showing what\u2019s possible<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Share in communities that love AI photos<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p class=\"p3\">Credits work across all AI tools on Photo AI.<\/p><p class=\"p3\"><strong>Start inviting and earn free credits today:<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"p1\">Sign up to <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq11\">Photo AI<\/a> \u2192 Click the logo \u2192 Referral program \u2192 Copy your link.<\/p><p class=\"p1\">Happy creating!<\/p><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/ai-video-generator">
							Turn images into stunning AI videos with Photo AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Turn images into stunning AI videos with Photo AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>With AI-generated video technology rapidly evolving, it\u2019s now possible to turn a single image into a cinematic video clip in seconds, with no editing skills. Whether you\u2019re a content creator, marketer, or just experimenting, Photo AI makes the process fast, easy, and insanely fun.<\/p><p>In this guide, we\u2019ll walk you through how to go from a static photo to a vivid, moving scene using <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq3\">Photo AI<\/a>\u2019s Image to Video feature.<\/p><h2 id=\"sdq1bl5pytz\" data-toc-id=\"sdq1bl5pytz\">From AI photo to motion in 3 easy steps<\/h2><p>Turning your photo into a short video takes less than a minute. Here\u2019s how:<\/p><ol><li><p>Inside Photo AI, first take some photos of the scene you like. Either write your own prompt or use one of our 100s of photo packs.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684448f675dd25683c81b11c\/01974ace-b665-7546-9df6-e9e4d1e294aa\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuMzIuMTgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 15.32.18.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684448f675dd25683c81b11c\/01974ace-b665-7546-9df6-e9e4d1e294aa\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuMzIuMTgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b9b26798f05f293f69b64ede0f9f68c9b5f02717409a60802a93884c141e32b3\"><\/li><li><p>Once you see a photo you\u2019d like to turn into a video, hover over it and tap [ Make video ].<\/p><p><br>You\u2019ll see a popup that lets you write a prompt which controls what happens in the scene, the motion of the camera and style:<\/p><p><br>\u201ccamera slowly zooms out and shows model standing in room while wind blows from outside\u201d<\/p><p><br>Where \u201cmodel\u201d references your AI model you created.<br><\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684448f675dd25683c81b11c\/01974acf-88ed-7577-a217-6f8fa68e51cf\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuMzEuNDEucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 15.31.41.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684448f675dd25683c81b11c\/01974acf-88ed-7577-a217-6f8fa68e51cf\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuMzEuNDEucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=499613583c65459d19ac76e5995031be7fc4c2c976e192541e3fbde7641be7a9\"><\/li><\/ol><ol start=\"3\"><li><p>It will then take a minute or so and your video is done!<br><br><\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGFkNy00ODA0LTc4NDItOWJkOC05NWRjNjA0NzUyMGMiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDQ0OGY2NzVkZDI1NjgzYzgxYjExYyIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTMwNzMxMn0.Pm0EkyWWLrQopF42corm-Vv0_mAd-KT8UIXdc_Xgt_c\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGFkNy00ODA0LTc4NDItOWJkOC05NWRjNjA0NzUyMGMiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ0NDhmNjc1ZGQyNTY4M2M4MWIxMWMiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.5Q0btTN_Te9VsvRgRYhfqEPNyOL9bVTEhu3fL4XIdDA\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><\/li><\/ol><h2 id=\"fq6s5iippts\" data-toc-id=\"fq6s5iippts\">Upload your own images to turn into a video<\/h2><p>With Photo AI you can also upload your own images (like real photos you made) and turn them into a video in a similar way.<\/p><ol><li><p>First go to [ Import into gallery ] and select your image.<br><\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684448f675dd25683c81b11c\/01974ad9-367a-76c8-9f11-237a3a382537\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuNDMuNTAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 15.43.50.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684448f675dd25683c81b11c\/01974ad9-367a-76c8-9f11-237a3a382537\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuNDMuNTAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=7de05919125bccaa8579d26047784acb5b8d86ec9de156a7baa664ce5550164a\"><p><br><\/p><\/li><li><p>Then once it shows up in the gallery, hover over the image and tap [ Make video ].<br><\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684448f675dd25683c81b11c\/01974ad9-9d7a-7ea3-9701-042ca728a230\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMzQuMDgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-06 at 21.34.08.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684448f675dd25683c81b11c\/01974ad9-9d7a-7ea3-9701-042ca728a230\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMzQuMDgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=95a2221da0b6ddd9388f1b94a9f5ad8fb01115e07a16f5e29c1758622971047e\"><\/li><\/ol><p>Just like before, you\u2019ll see a popup that lets you write a prompt which controls what happens in the scene, the motion of the camera and style:<\/p><p>\u201cThe camera slowly zooms out to reveal the model in a futuristic city glowing at night\u201d<\/p><ol start=\"3\"><li><p>It will then take a minute or so and your video is done!<\/p><\/li><\/ol><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGM2NS1lNWUwLTc3MDktOWUzYy04MGJlNDljODM3NGEiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDQ0OGY2NzVkZDI1NjgzYzgxYjExYyIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTMzMzQzNn0.Boaky4aptsmsn9B4HGS5Iehulkl69ECucBtI080FKpM\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749307479-bccab747dd31827d39baf6dec0c82a6f-1 (1).mp4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGM2NS1lNWUwLTc3MDktOWUzYy04MGJlNDljODM3NGEiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ0NDhmNjc1ZGQyNTY4M2M4MWIxMWMiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.LXQA5SVwlxR9w0rzwC3N55X-kCy4565fPyTLACOgI_c\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"ywq2mxrs403\" data-toc-id=\"ywq2mxrs403\">Photo AI uses the latest world-class AI video models<\/h2><p>Photo AI gives you access to the latest in cutting-edge video models and the moment a new video model is launched we usually have it available in our app within hours:<\/p><ul><li><p>Kling<\/p><\/li><li><p>Hailuo AI\u2019s Minimax<\/p><\/li><li><p>Pixverse<\/p><\/li><li><p>Google\u2019s Veo<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>Photo AI auto-selects the best model available at any time and because AI models are quite safety sensitive, will fallback to every single model until it finds one that can do what you prompt it to do. Giving it one of the highest success % rates of any AI app for image-to-video.<\/p><h2 id=\"ym22xmys01l\" data-toc-id=\"ym22xmys01l\"><strong>Smooth motion, high quality, instant results<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\">With Photo AI\u2019s video engine, you get:<\/p><ul><li><p class=\"p1\"><strong>5\u201310 second clips<\/strong> with fluid, cinematic motion<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Zero video editing experience required<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Instant preview and downloads<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p class=\"p3\">Whether you\u2019re turning a selfie into a dramatic scene or animating your artwork, Photo AI delivers unmatched quality in just a few clicks.<\/p><h2 id=\"bykdbt50pf1\" data-toc-id=\"bykdbt50pf1\"><strong>Final thoughts<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\">AI video used to require complex tools and hours of editing. Now, with Photo AI\u2019s <strong>Image to Video<\/strong> feature, you can go from static to cinematic in under a minute.<\/p><p class=\"p3\">Take an AI photo or upload your own image, write a prompt, and let the AI handle the rest.<\/p><p class=\"p3\">\u2192 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq3\">Try Image to Video now on Photo AI<\/a><\/p><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/i-used-the-wrong-card-and-want-a-refund-and-switch-it-to-my-company-card">
							I used the wrong card and want a refund and switch it to my company card						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "I used the wrong card and want a refund and switch it to my company card",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>The best is to self-refund your account, then cancel it, then sign up again with a new email and your correct card.<\/p><p>We cannot refund you or switch your card ourselves.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/batch-try-on-clothes">
							Batch Try On Clothes with Photo AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Batch Try On Clothes with Photo AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p class=\"p3\">Want to see your AI model wearing different clothing? Scroll down to the Try On Clothing mode on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq13\">Photo AI<\/a> and there you can now upload multiple photos to try on clothes in batch.<\/p><p class=\"p3\">This is particularly useful if you\u2019re a fashion designer, label or store and have a new collection you need to have try on photos of fast.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/01977910-8b35-7b38-8265-c32e2d15049e\/b64u-YmF0Y2h0cnlvbmZhcS53ZWJw.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"batchtryonfaq.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/01977910-8b35-7b38-8265-c32e2d15049e\/b64u-YmF0Y2h0cnlvbmZhcS53ZWJw.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=c831575b2f46ff54148a781c44499c6c53b4fbfdee6965f1076d25dc0aa6beae\"><h2 id=\"xi0e8qpql5a\" data-toc-id=\"xi0e8qpql5a\">Step 1: Create or select your AI model<\/h2><p>Go to [ Create new AI model ] in the sidebar. Upload around 20 photos of your model, this could be yourself or someone you\u2019ve hired.<\/p><p>In about a minute, Photo AI will train a photorealistic, personalized AI model that looks just like them.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/019778fd-a26c-7721-b35c-e38ce8423298\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.40.30.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/019778fd-a26c-7721-b35c-e38ce8423298\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=e812a16af3fa82ab5f3dc3fea78fb3b361fbdc716c2687c6e7409e3e25b80c5f\"><p>You can reuse this model to try on different outfits endlessly.<\/p><h2 id=\"l43tmaloo47\" data-toc-id=\"l43tmaloo47\"><strong>Step 2: Go to [ Try on clothes ] in the sidebar<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">This opens the try on panel where you can upload your photos:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/019778fd-1f62-71b9-bdfe-6d90bdc9fae9\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuNDMuNDUucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-16 at 15.43.45.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/019778fd-1f62-71b9-bdfe-6d90bdc9fae9\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuNDMuNDUucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=51bd5c855971ccd1ac7752ce972a93a132269398eea5ecd84a4b49f642e4758c\"><h2 id=\"kz4c66a75c3\" data-toc-id=\"kz4c66a75c3\"><strong>Step 3: Upload multiple images<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Upload multiple photos \u2014 clothing laid flat, or worn by someone else:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/019778fd-3eb0-74ba-8c50-f59e288e125b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuNDIuMzUucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-16 at 15.42.35.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/019778fd-3eb0-74ba-8c50-f59e288e125b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuNDIuMzUucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=ce2bfa3da2f13bf5406cd50698574deea67aaff2333c5c7c521b6a498a6f3407\"><h2 id=\"w4y2aqaepyq\" data-toc-id=\"w4y2aqaepyq\"><strong>Step 4: Tap [ Take photo ]<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Each photo gets processed individually with your AI model wearing the clothes, producing consistent photos for your fashion label or store.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/01977901-4d67-70f7-97e9-db51b6b9fc03\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuNDkuMjEucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-16 at 15.49.21.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685020029ae2254138d9033b\/01977901-4d67-70f7-97e9-db51b6b9fc03\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuNDkuMjEucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=e65441592f367ded3d2b9ce1f8621b352f0cf4429e4f046f1d0ad13529bacdcf\"><h2 id=\"m52qwpoydcl\" data-toc-id=\"m52qwpoydcl\"><strong>Bonus: Turn them into videos<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\">Hover over any remixed image and click [Make video] to animate the outfit in motion.<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NzkxNy0xNTc5LTc0NjUtOGM1NS00ZjQ4ZjhiNmRlNmEiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NTAyMDAyOWFlMjI1NDEzOGQ5MDMzYiIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc1MDA4MzI0NX0.3rOpu8eEpyiBxSB04lf5dX0ulIqleJz4ulCbKiVo4Uo\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1750082460-9c0cb0e9fd05e20f4f572d1eb2544ba5-1.mp4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NzkxNy0xNTc5LTc0NjUtOGM1NS00ZjQ4ZjhiNmRlNmEiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODUwMjAwMjlhZTIyNTQxMzhkOTAzM2IiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.Vp6OcOnEaLa56pg8X38I7A0ZAdQcA8Af35dGRYp_bwU\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"8y564lz2tzm\" data-toc-id=\"8y564lz2tzm\">What\u2019s Batch Try On Clothes useful for?<\/h2><p class=\"p3\">\u2705 Great for Shopify sellers, fashion brands, or indie designers<\/p><p class=\"p3\">\u2705 Saves the cost of physical samples and photo shoots<\/p><p class=\"p3\">\u2705 Lets you test outfit ideas instantly on real-looking people<\/p><p class=\"p3\">\u2705 Run it on an entire collection of clothes without uploading individual pieces<\/p><p class=\"p3\">Try batch try on clothes now in <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq13\">Photo AI<\/a>. Only on Premium and Ultra plans.<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NzkxNi1jNzI4LTdkZTAtODY2My1hMjQ2ZmY2YTgwNDciLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NTAyMDAyOWFlMjI1NDEzOGQ5MDMzYiIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc1MDA4MzIyNX0.vAFvH9fyRw6Dk32k9UwkOvAXVwbLNGTKvlzQKA0isLo\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NzkxNi1jNzI4LTdkZTAtODY2My1hMjQ2ZmY2YTgwNDciLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODUwMjAwMjlhZTIyNTQxMzhkOTAzM2IiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.aNmXgwt89wTpqHdGr-sD4doqMTQ9VnohHv0hsicmhTQ\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NzkxNi05ZWFhLTc4NDctYWZlNi0xYjU3NGNmNzQ3YzYiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NTAyMDAyOWFlMjI1NDEzOGQ5MDMzYiIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc1MDA4MzIxNX0.3hhPadEwwlOQqGSBiEKSdn1IUCVs6NyPl1oIETH3fN0\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NzkxNi05ZWFhLTc4NDctYWZlNi0xYjU3NGNmNzQ3YzYiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODUwMjAwMjlhZTIyNTQxMzhkOTAzM2IiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.ouhG6mVbQijBNY_bas8W1-MTuKUKFZJDw6dRW2eeUYI\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><p class=\"p3\"><\/p><p class=\"p3\"><\/p><p class=\"p3\"><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
