						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/nano-banana-pro-image-generator-on-photo-ai">
							Nano Banana Pro image generator on Photo AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Nano Banana Pro image generator on Photo AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Photo AI now supports Google\u2019s new \ud83c\udf4c Nano Banana Pro image model to generate photos of people with.<\/p><p>What\u2019s good is it\u2019s less restricted than using it with Gemini and it\u2019s specialized with Photo AI\u2019s secret sauce for creating realistic photos (and videos) of people.<\/p><p>To use it is very simple:<\/p><h1 id=\"krficaezp80\" data-toc-id=\"krficaezp80\">1) Sign up to Photo AI<\/h1><p>First sign up to <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\">Photo AI<\/a>, you can use your email or Google account to sign up.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6937c2002bce2ac8424471b3\/019b01cf-d7e5-7618-8b4f-f9832ecd5e76\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMTItMDkgYXQgMTQuMzIuMzAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-12-09 at 14.32.30.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6937c2002bce2ac8424471b3\/019b01cf-d7e5-7618-8b4f-f9832ecd5e76\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMTItMDkgYXQgMTQuMzIuMzAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b194df7e95c8df94eb41a7428274e45badc3701e5947addba211995605239ec6\"><h1 id=\"yy5qt5wd8ka\" data-toc-id=\"yy5qt5wd8ka\">2) Create your first AI model<\/h1><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6937c2002bce2ac8424471b3\/019b01d1-9363-75d7-9733-907b25b2dcf5\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMjguNTgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-06 at 21.28.58.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6937c2002bce2ac8424471b3\/019b01d1-9363-75d7-9733-907b25b2dcf5\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMjguNTgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=379b45fe43243da31862e68d5ab3a8422899906866d5ce955aff6dbf6fa54938\"><h1 id=\"toddclk27es\" data-toc-id=\"toddclk27es\">3) Select \ud83c\udf4c Nano Banana Pro as your model<\/h1><p>Under the [ Take photo ] button in Photo AI, press the toggle and it will switch from Hyper Realism to Nano Banana Pro as your preferred model.<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTliMDFkMy0yZjZhLTdhYjAtYTc1Yy04ZTAwZTllMjljYWUiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY5MzdjMjAwMmJjZTJhYzg0MjQ0NzFiMyIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc2NTI2MjIxN30.Kq4e_fjeKhf3LqVySjVaxt9OUcu7GW8wwFBrFvHFx1Y\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTliMDFkMy0yZjZhLTdhYjAtYTc1Yy04ZTAwZTllMjljYWUiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2OTM3YzIwMDJiY2UyYWM4NDI0NDcxYjMiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.y2zLOSWkX3XIeeFHpM0NTa6w9sOJypeaReK0KeWNrXw\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h1 id=\"fq4820d1cyy\" data-toc-id=\"fq4820d1cyy\">4) Done!<\/h1><p>And there you go! Every photo you now generate will be using Nano Banana Pro \ud83d\ude0a<\/p><p>You can now also use JSON prompts with Nano Banana Pro like the one below to create a very detailed photograph like this<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6937c2002bce2ac8424471b3\/019b020b-00b8-7fa8-bafc-6ca575b0e0c6\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMTItMDkgYXQgMTUuMzYuMzIucG5n.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6937c2002bce2ac8424471b3\/019b020b-00b8-7fa8-bafc-6ca575b0e0c6\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMTItMDkgYXQgMTUuMzYuMzIucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=177484c72c37c49912bea8c251669f03cdaee1256b50ff591c3f0b50a8ab8fda\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-12-09 at 15.36.32.png\"><p><\/p><multicode-component data=\"[{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;JSON prompt&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:&quot;{\\n  \\&quot;task_configuration\\&quot;: {\\n    \\&quot;task_type\\&quot;: \\&quot;screen_simulation_photorealism\\&quot;,\\n    \\&quot;target_model\\&quot;: \\&quot;SDXL_1.0_Refiner\\&quot;,\\n    \\&quot;aspect_ratio\\&quot;: \\&quot;3:4\\&quot;,\\n    \\&quot;resolution\\&quot;: {\\n      \\&quot;width\\&quot;: 1152,\\n      \\&quot;height\\&quot;: 1536\\n    }\\n  },\\n  \\&quot;visual_hierarchy\\&quot;: {\\n    \\&quot;layer_1_physical_macro\\&quot;: {\\n      \\&quot;camera_angle\\&quot;: \\&quot;Downward-angled, high-angle\\&quot;,\\n      \\&quot;framing\\&quot;: \\&quot;MacBook screen filling 95% of frame\\&quot;,\\n      \\&quot;surface_imperfections\\&quot;: [\\n        \\&quot;subtle pixel-grid texture (moire)\\&quot;,\\n        \\&quot;tiny dust particles on glass\\&quot;,\\n        \\&quot;faint ambient light reflection on glossy screen\\&quot;,\\n        \\&quot;fingerprint smudges\\&quot;\\n      ],\\n      \\&quot;foreground_anchor\\&quot;: \\&quot;Thin strip of physical keyboard visible at lower edge\\&quot;\\n    },\\n    \\&quot;layer_2_digital_interface\\&quot;: {\\n      \\&quot;theme\\&quot;: \\&quot;Dark Mode (macOS)\\&quot;,\\n      \\&quot;window_layout\\&quot;: {\\n        \\&quot;left_panel\\&quot;: \\&quot;Spotify 'Liked Songs' playlist (dimmed)\\&quot;,\\n        \\&quot;right_panel\\&quot;: \\&quot;Photo Booth live-preview window (dominant focus)\\&quot;\\n      }\\n    },\\n    \\&quot;layer_3_nested_subject_content\\&quot;: {\\n      \\&quot;context\\&quot;: \\&quot;Inside the Photo Booth window\\&quot;,\\n      \\&quot;environment\\&quot;: \\&quot;Dim bedroom, off-plain background, rumpled bedding\\&quot;,\\n      \\&quot;lighting_simulation\\&quot;: \\&quot;Cool screen glow mixed with warm skin tones, deep nocturnal shadows\\&quot;,\\n      \\&quot;subjects\\&quot;: {\\n        \\&quot;shared_attributes\\&quot;: [\\n          \\&quot;Oversized black hoodies\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;Hoods pushed back (faces fully visible)\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;Reclining pose\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;Looking at screen\\&quot;\\n        ],\\n        \\&quot;subject_a_guy\\&quot;: {\\n          \\&quot;identity_target\\&quot;: \\&quot;reference_image_male.jpg\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;action\\&quot;: \\&quot;Holding phone in right hand with clear reflective case\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;position\\&quot;: \\&quot;Right\/Center\\&quot;\\n        },\\n        \\&quot;subject_b_girl\\&quot;: {\\n          \\&quot;identity_target\\&quot;: \\&quot;reference_image_female.jpg\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;action\\&quot;: \\&quot;Resting closely beside Subject A\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;position\\&quot;: \\&quot;Left\/Center\\&quot;\\n        }\\n      }\\n    }\\n  },\\n  \\&quot;prompt_assembly\\&quot;: {\\n    \\&quot;positive_prompt\\&quot;: \\&quot;Hyper-realistic downward shot of a MacBook screen. The screen surface has visible dust, pixel grid, and reflection. The screen displays a Photo Booth window showing a couple in a dark room. [Subject Descriptions]. They are wearing black hoodies. The lighting is low-key, candid, nocturnal, blue-ish screen glow. High fidelity, raw photo, unedited.\\&quot;,\\n    \\&quot;negative_prompt\\&quot;: \\&quot;vector art, screenshot, flat digital image, clean glass, perfect screen, daylight, bright studio lights, cartoon, 3d render, painting, watermark\\&quot;\\n  },\\n  \\&quot;identity_preservation_settings\\&quot;: {\\n    \\&quot;strictness_level\\&quot;: \\&quot;CRITICAL\\&quot;,\\n    \\&quot;methodology\\&quot;: {\\n      \\&quot;face_restoration\\&quot;: false,\\n      \\&quot;note\\&quot;: \\&quot;Disable generic face restorers (CodeFormer) to avoid 'plastic' look. Use IP-Adapter.\\&quot;,\\n      \\&quot;control_net_stack\\&quot;: [\\n        {\\n          \\&quot;unit\\&quot;: \\&quot;ControlNet_Tile\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;weight\\&quot;: 0.4,\\n          \\&quot;purpose\\&quot;: \\&quot;To maintain the text\/interface sharpness\\&quot;\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\&quot;unit\\&quot;: \\&quot;IP-Adapter_FaceID_Plus\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;weight\\&quot;: 0.95,\\n          \\&quot;region_mask\\&quot;: \\&quot;Photo Booth Window Area Only\\&quot;,\\n          \\&quot;purpose\\&quot;: \\&quot;To force exact facial identity match for both subjects\\&quot;\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  },\\n  \\&quot;rendering_parameters\\&quot;: {\\n    \\&quot;sampler\\&quot;: \\&quot;DPM++ 3M SDE Exponential\\&quot;,\\n    \\&quot;steps\\&quot;: 40,\\n    \\&quot;cfg_scale\\&quot;: 5.5,\\n    \\&quot;denoising_strength\\&quot;: 0.35\\n  }\\n}&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;48df3e25-8890-42a8-b925-6c43ba83c3b9&quot;,&quot;language&quot;:&quot;javascript&quot;}]\" activecode=\"48df3e25-8890-42a8-b925-6c43ba83c3b9\"><\/multicode-component><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/can-i-use-photo-ai-to-put-clothes-on-models-for-my-shopify-store">
							Can I use Photo AI to put clothes on models for my Shopify store?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Can I use Photo AI to put clothes on models for my Shopify store?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">Yes!<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">You can upload any clothes and the model will wear them for you.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">We use the latest state of the art try on models.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">We have many customers like fashion designers and dropshippers that already use it everyday for Shopify stores. They can design clothes virtually and already put them on models without ever producing the clothes!<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">Even cooler, with the [ Make video ] feature you can turn your models wearing your clothes into videos!<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">Only for Premium and Ultra subscribers.<\/span><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/can-i-delete-my-data">
							Can I delete my data?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Can I delete my data?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Yes, you can delete your photos in the gallery: hover over a photo, and click the trash bin in the top right to delete it. Deleted photos are permanently deleted after 30 days. <\/p><p>For models it's the same, go to the top left model selector at \"Select model\", and hover over a model, in the top right of the model click the trash bin to delete it. <\/p><p>If you cancel your subscription your data is completely deleted after 90 days.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/is-there-a-photo-ai-ios-app">
							Is there a Photo AI iOS app?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Is there a Photo AI iOS app?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">We did have one but not anymore. It's easier to focus all my energy on just the Photo AI website and make that the best AI photo and video generator out there.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">If you see one called Photo AI, it\u2019s a rip-off and not related to us!<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">Existing Photo AI iOS subscriptions have all automatically ended.<\/span><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/what-type-of-photos-should-i-upload-for-creating-an-ai-model">
							What type of photos should I upload for creating an AI model?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "What type of photos should I upload for creating an AI model?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>We recommend uploading photos with high variety, a mix of close-up selfies and full body shots in a variety of places, angles, clothes and expressions. Do not upload photos with low variety, group photos, other people, sunglasses, hats, photos where your face is cut off or not visible.<\/p><p>If you\u2019re creating an AI influencer from scratch, you don\u2019t need to upload any photos though. You just design a new persona based on how you want them to look!<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/i-cancelled-photo-ai-but-am-still-being-charged">
							I cancelled Photo AI but am still being charged						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "I cancelled Photo AI but am still being charged",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>In 100% of cases when this happens, you\u2019ve signed up with a different email addresses and you canceled your subscription on one account. But there is still an ongoing subscription on the other.<\/p><p>To resolve this:<\/p><p>First find the right account email address by searching your inbox for emails from Stripe with subject \u201cYour receipt from Photo AI\u201d and see what email they are sent to.<\/p><p>Then go to <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"http:\/\/photoai.com\/billing\">photoai.com\/billing<\/a> and log in with that email address. This is NOT the regular Photo AI login, this is specifically the login to the Stripe Customer Portal where you can self-manage your subscriptions.<\/p><p>Once inside there you\u2019ll see your active subscriptions and can cancel them!<\/p><img src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/01945693-98d6-7f15-9ccb-9222bcad7e3f.png\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/ai-photo-editor">
							How to edit your photos with AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to edit your photos with AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want to change something in your photo? Add objects, remove them, or even change the entire scene \u2014 all with a single sentence. With <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq6\">Photo AI<\/a>\u2019s <strong>Magic Edit<\/strong> feature, it\u2019s insanely easy.<\/p><p class=\"p1\">Whether you want to swap a drink, change your background, or fix a small detail, you just describe the change and Photo AI does the rest.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f94-3764-7397-8994-fc6da1a77f2b\/b64u-MTc0OTMyOTkzNi1lOWFmNmJjMjY1YTU0YWNjZjQ5NjdhM2ZmNmJjZWFhNi0yLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749329936-e9af6bc265a54accf4967a3ff6bceaa6-2.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f94-3764-7397-8994-fc6da1a77f2b\/b64u-MTc0OTMyOTkzNi1lOWFmNmJjMjY1YTU0YWNjZjQ5NjdhM2ZmNmJjZWFhNi0yLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=3a35049dd319e1f7a610516dcb7d753a79e903a62544054f46a5079df62847e6\"><h2 id=\"riakzrirwra\" data-toc-id=\"riakzrirwra\">What is Magic Edit<strong>?<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\">Magic Edit is a simple tool that lets you modify any photo using text. Instead of Photoshop or masking tools, you just type what you want, like:<\/p><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">\u201cChange the wine to sparkling water with lemon\u201d<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">\u201cMake it sunset on the beach\u201d<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">\u201cRemove the person in the background\u201d<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p class=\"p3\">Photo AI analyzes your photo and applies the changes instantly with AI-powered image editing.<\/p><h2 id=\"yek72c03zya\" data-toc-id=\"yek72c03zya\"><strong>How to use Magic Edit<\/strong><\/h2><h2 id=\"ysrktiy53ll\" data-toc-id=\"ysrktiy53ll\"><strong>Step 1: Hover over your photo<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Inside your Photo AI gallery, hover over the image you want to change.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f86-f625-7a70-bded-6d8cd7999fd9\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuMzIuMDYucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 13.32.06.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f86-f625-7a70-bded-6d8cd7999fd9\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuMzIuMDYucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=3927ff7f779e07a7bdef256f0af6f928b1ce02342362f4ee9aa03debf59ff5f9\"><h2 id=\"w8qrta2li2e\" data-toc-id=\"w8qrta2li2e\"><strong>Step 2: Click [ Magic Edit ]<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">A button will appear \u2014 click it to open the edit popup.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f87-3988-7838-8876-3fa6f165929d\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuMzIuMjUucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 13.32.25.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f87-3988-7838-8876-3fa6f165929d\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuMzIuMjUucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=fb52581fa631837aa4df2d22d4c49fbb9ce2b982c2844ddb1f62c2f7443b7270\"><h2 id=\"35mlozo88kr\" data-toc-id=\"35mlozo88kr\"><strong>Step 3: Type your change<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">In the popup, describe what you want to change. Be clear and specific \u2014 the more detailed, the better.<\/p><p class=\"p4\">Examples:<\/p><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">\u201cPut me in a private jet drinking sparkling water with a half cut lemon\u201d<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">\u201cChange my outfit to a black suit\u201d<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">\u201cMake the sky cloudy with soft light\u201d<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">\u201cChange my photo to anime\u201d<\/p><\/li><\/ul><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f87-d727-7985-8be4-6dbfa76e10b6\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuMzIuNTUucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 13.32.55.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f87-d727-7985-8be4-6dbfa76e10b6\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuMzIuNTUucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=0a3bb963bb50198e1b12b2542358b1eeaf0b5c0f08ec5980f1ba03b399d95d70\"><h2 id=\"6zxyts1ywpr\" data-toc-id=\"6zxyts1ywpr\">Step 4: See the result!<\/h2><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8c-0178-7d5f-afbc-87bff52785ef\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuMzcuMzUucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 13.37.35.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8c-0178-7d5f-afbc-87bff52785ef\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuMzcuMzUucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=2a9f42a31c22931a43283acbcf65413fa7e48a7ce54367920982285a503a3229\"><p>So we went from sitting in a restaurant eating:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8c-51a6-79b6-9e67-cc295b94db79\/b64u-MTc0OTMyOTkzNi1lOWFmNmJjMjY1YTU0YWNjZjQ5NjdhM2ZmNmJjZWFhNi0yLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749329936-e9af6bc265a54accf4967a3ff6bceaa6-2.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8c-51a6-79b6-9e67-cc295b94db79\/b64u-MTc0OTMyOTkzNi1lOWFmNmJjMjY1YTU0YWNjZjQ5NjdhM2ZmNmJjZWFhNi0yLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=1e5adade0676a2edd83f45df0e6da299a2393e91f977b551357f6c7fda78d54a\"><p>To sitting in a private jet with sparkling water and half a cut lemon:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8c-7c6e-7077-a26a-2c315c61436f\/b64u-MTc0OTM4NjAxNC1jYTlmZGI2MjMzZDdkNjUzMWY3NDRhODM2ZDA0NTg2My0xLmpwZWc.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749386014-ca9fdb6233d7d6531f744a836d045863-1.jpeg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8c-7c6e-7077-a26a-2c315c61436f\/b64u-MTc0OTM4NjAxNC1jYTlmZGI2MjMzZDdkNjUzMWY3NDRhODM2ZDA0NTg2My0xLmpwZWc.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b36dbcb0e152312b365d368bae2aef05ca4880f6c190154f722cc5cec3051146\"><h2 id=\"dlwlds36dtl\" data-toc-id=\"dlwlds36dtl\">Possibilities are endless<\/h2><p>You can change anything in a photo, and even change the entire style of a photo, like here \u201cput in anime style\u201d:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8d-c587-7153-8f47-1d46cc58eb93\/b64u-MTc0OTM4NjM0NS1iNDZhOTA5NGNiM2Q4Y2FkMDYyMjA4MGUxNzIzMjdhMi0xLmpwZWc.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749386345-b46a9094cb3d8cad0622080e172327a2-1.jpeg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8d-c587-7153-8f47-1d46cc58eb93\/b64u-MTc0OTM4NjM0NS1iNDZhOTA5NGNiM2Q4Y2FkMDYyMjA4MGUxNzIzMjdhMi0xLmpwZWc.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=2068ca0e03a46dd0e79dfee6362c14913b8aabf583c3e5693b31bc067eba326b\"><p>And then you can even move the camera position (although this doesn\u2019t always change the background perfectly but you can try), like here \u201cside view\u201d:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8e-666b-754c-a841-9aee7db312d0\/b64u-MTc0OTM4NjM4Ny0yMjFmMWMxZmVhMmQwN2Q2ZDQ2MDkzMzVmNzgyNmUyYy0xLmpwZWc.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749386387-221f1c1fea2d07d6d4609335f7826e2c-1.jpeg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8e-666b-754c-a841-9aee7db312d0\/b64u-MTc0OTM4NjM4Ny0yMjFmMWMxZmVhMmQwN2Q2ZDQ2MDkzMzVmNzgyNmUyYy0xLmpwZWc.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=e9302bae08d13f23ed26daec1099928738238c0582dc5233274570ab7584b392\"><p>And then try change it back to a photo, \u201cchange it a photo\u201d:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8e-cf18-791d-a3d8-f3eb1b952e39\/b64u-MTc0OTM4NjQzMy1kZTI3NDJhZDFlNjYxYzFhODc1NzI2MzIxMTEzMDU4MC0xLmpwZWc.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749386433-de2742ad1e661c1a8757263211130580-1.jpeg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f8e-cf18-791d-a3d8-f3eb1b952e39\/b64u-MTc0OTM4NjQzMy1kZTI3NDJhZDFlNjYxYzFhODc1NzI2MzIxMTEzMDU4MC0xLmpwZWc.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=8aeaff697f3f958fbb082f33db91225234d29cce497abe068a2bb1cdaa032105\"><p>Magic Edit does NOT use your AI model so you will lose any likeness\/resemblance at this point, to get that back you can remix it though (which does use your AI model), by tapping [ Remix ] on the photo and then it\u2019ll look like you again:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f90-4742-79a3-8289-a7e7f306744a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuNDIuMDkucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 13.42.09.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684581e5872272f45d2e55ab\/01974f90-4742-79a3-8289-a7e7f306744a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTMuNDIuMDkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b624e7c89b0d5dd4b5e494be7de95238b5d9dbc9f36b123771c2fa0ccbff3db0\"><p>As I said the possibilities are pretty endless, try it!<\/p><h2 id=\"qso7cc7b4b2\" data-toc-id=\"qso7cc7b4b2\"><strong>Why it\u2019s powerful<\/strong><\/h2><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">No Photoshop or design tools needed<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Natural language \u2014 just describe what you want<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Fast, fun, and flexible for creative edits<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Possible to make camera perspective changes like \u201cchange to side view\u201d<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Complete style changes like \u201cchange to anime style\u201d<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>Try [ Magic Edit ] now on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq6\">Photo AI<\/a><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/uncrop-ai">
							Uncrop & expand images with Photo AI's Zoom Out feature						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Uncrop & expand images with Photo AI's Zoom Out feature",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Ever wish you could zoom out of a photo that was shot too tight or extend the background beyond the frame? With Photo AI\u2019s Zoom Out feature, you can do exactly that. It uses generative AI to uncrop and expand your images realistically, filling in extra space that looks like it was always there.<\/p><p>Perfect for fixing awkward crops, generating landscape shots, or giving more room around your subject.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bae-4c19-7114-8697-254146b86966\/b64u-MTc0OTMxOTk5NS01ZjM4ZmRkYWU3NjU1MzhkMDFjMjg5M2U5YWQ1ZDUyYy0yLmpwZw.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749319995-5f38fddae765538d01c2893e9ad5d52c-2.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bae-4c19-7114-8697-254146b86966\/b64u-MTc0OTMxOTk5NS01ZjM4ZmRkYWU3NjU1MzhkMDFjMjg5M2U5YWQ1ZDUyYy0yLmpwZw.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=5ce252e07b59d1d73e52accb3faef86893848d81a021d24d69f785cf336017b2\"><h2 id=\"7erd722amb8\" data-toc-id=\"7erd722amb8\">What is Zoom Out?<\/h2><p class=\"p3\"><strong>Zoom Out<\/strong> is Photo AI\u2019s image uncropping tool. It uses AI to extend your original image outward, generating new background and scene content to fill the space while keeping your subject exactly the same.<\/p><p class=\"p3\">It\u2019s like reverse-cropping: instead of cutting out, you grow the image.<\/p><h2 id=\"1xzw6ba6cro\" data-toc-id=\"1xzw6ba6cro\"><strong>When to use it:<\/strong><\/h2><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">You want to turn a tight headshot into a portrait<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">You need a horizontal version of a vertical photo<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">A model or product is cut off in the frame<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">You want to create more whitespace or background for design<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h2 id=\"qo3zpdefkpt\" data-toc-id=\"qo3zpdefkpt\"><strong>Step 1: Select your image<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Choose any generated photo inside your Photo AI account that you want to expand.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bab-096d-7fdc-a4e9-4fefb48241ae\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMzIuNTkucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.32.59.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bab-096d-7fdc-a4e9-4fefb48241ae\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMzIuNTkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=3672366c8cf64a31dcf071a1a7ac8439c74d1f55e3f488459b3b6dc380cdb4ea\"><h2 id=\"dzmymosesim\" data-toc-id=\"dzmymosesim\"><strong>Step 2: Click [ Zoom Out ]<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">You\u2019ll find it in the hover actions under the image, or in the image actions menu.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974baa-d0d6-7abc-9e15-8ae60b41ea73\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMzIuMzMucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.32.33.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974baa-d0d6-7abc-9e15-8ae60b41ea73\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMzIuMzMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=61d794758a0eb3dea8bfd27ac1ce3452389ef5af02cf1e533a6a6b158015d0e7\"><h2 id=\"qmb2rpiwef6\" data-toc-id=\"qmb2rpiwef6\"><strong>Step 3: See the result<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">In seconds, Photo AI gives you an expanded version with new background and realistic edge content that blends seamlessly with your original photo.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bab-67c7-71a8-aa68-1d357ab4300c\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMzMuMjcucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.33.27.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bab-67c7-71a8-aa68-1d357ab4300c\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMzMuMjcucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=4b4e534f3f9e45f69c3d0b246599559a6a8c362078d94c8a8a0bb110518a2b27\"><h2 id=\"wxf6te37s6a\" data-toc-id=\"wxf6te37s6a\">Step 4 (optionally): Do it again and again and again<\/h2><p>You can keep zooming out essentially forever. Just keep tapping [ Zoom out ] on the new zoomed out photo every time it\u2019s done.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bac-7593-7f90-afe9-0b7e1fd71e48\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMzQuMTkucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.34.19.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bac-7593-7f90-afe9-0b7e1fd71e48\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMzQuMTkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=d8141928c09850fb1b9cad61c8128f0240421068272c74c0608341aed1df1c0c\"><p>You go from this:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bad-21b5-7055-b5d5-b703e54d6aa5\/b64u-MTc0OTMxOTk5NS01ZjM4ZmRkYWU3NjU1MzhkMDFjMjg5M2U5YWQ1ZDUyYy0yLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749319995-5f38fddae765538d01c2893e9ad5d52c-2.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bad-21b5-7055-b5d5-b703e54d6aa5\/b64u-MTc0OTMxOTk5NS01ZjM4ZmRkYWU3NjU1MzhkMDFjMjg5M2U5YWQ1ZDUyYy0yLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=7e01a812cd0e18ca8d655d8607d7dc1a1dfb5731a1f16534831cb5d90d09678a\"><p>All the way to this:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bad-2544-761f-a70c-73f58054a5b2\/b64u-MTc0OTMyMTIyMi1iMTQ1YzkyNGUxYjM5MjFlMjkxOTRiZjA0MTE0ZTkyOC0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749321222-b145c924e1b3921e29194bf04114e928-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bad-2544-761f-a70c-73f58054a5b2\/b64u-MTc0OTMyMTIyMi1iMTQ1YzkyNGUxYjM5MjFlMjkxOTRiZjA0MTE0ZTkyOC0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=fc4e81f5f8ed6ee88489c118891dfac7d858d93e50c75ef1b742b51bbfd04089\"><h2 id=\"fq6s5iippts\" data-toc-id=\"fq6s5iippts\">Upload your own images to uncrop and expand<\/h2><p>With Photo AI you can also upload your own images (like real photos you made or literally any image you can think of) and uncrop them with [ Zoom out ]<\/p><ol><li><p>First go to [ Import into gallery ] and select your image.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bd7-4d5e-7120-b8a4-9b6d13cdbe2f\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuNDMuNTAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 15.43.50.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bd7-4d5e-7120-b8a4-9b6d13cdbe2f\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuNDMuNTAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=e9c32104775bd214d0b00d75c6cb05ebfa081950eacc62dfe4dd11e913d60261\"><p><\/p><\/li><li><p>Then once it shows up in the gallery, hover over the image and tap [ Zoom out ].<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bd7-4dd2-7bb1-920b-cb5953c624ea\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMzQuMDgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-06 at 21.34.08.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bd7-4dd2-7bb1-920b-cb5953c624ea\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMzQuMDgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b83499dd43579bac7df40ef52c3c051ef5c5e5356a9877f0ef385860ea320f2f\"><\/li><\/ol><p>It then starts processing:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bd8-96d0-7236-8c78-2316fccb3cf7\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMjAuMjIuNDcucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 20.22.47.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bd8-96d0-7236-8c78-2316fccb3cf7\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMjAuMjIuNDcucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=c01a487da173700d6ebd6b24cf34f6cc82fb9cf63aa5e7a8471cfdb2c82e8cbc\"><p>And then you have your zoomed out photo:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bd8-dbbc-7e78-aa0c-3e7606d771a1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMjAuMjMuMDcucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 20.23.07.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974bd8-dbbc-7e78-aa0c-3e7606d771a1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMjAuMjMuMDcucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=39a366fa95ca9d87c84765de735626fb16dd1544c721ccbdd55dc0739803ec51\"><p>And if you keep going:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974be1-51e9-7b52-aa7c-d4714bc0f32a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMjAuMzIuMTIucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 20.32.12.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974be1-51e9-7b52-aa7c-d4714bc0f32a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMjAuMzIuMTIucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=f7298de264c09809738a5e2e470fd9e98ab9ee3afe940ab2741a346411c611a2\"><p>So we can go from:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974be1-d563-7848-a480-70cbe1c66ce2\/b64u-MTc0OTMyNDEzNy05NTM1OTE3OTIxZTJhZmQxMDkwMGVmZDM5NzMzMTk1Mi0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749324137-9535917921e2afd10900efd397331952-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974be1-d563-7848-a480-70cbe1c66ce2\/b64u-MTc0OTMyNDEzNy05NTM1OTE3OTIxZTJhZmQxMDkwMGVmZDM5NzMzMTk1Mi0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=cd56aff6e76810c8626e691178bbfe3bf0fd40b71e3b10d7cfdc0dfb791ed448\"><p>all the way to:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974be1-aa45-7f1f-9747-97213ed085b9\/b64u-MTc0OTMyNDM5NC1iMTFiMTg4Yjk2NWNlMWE2ZGMzYWM2MmFlM2UyYTk4Ni0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749324394-b11b188b965ce1a6dc3ac62ae3e2a986-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68448307eac9f9fe31e7dc05\/01974be1-aa45-7f1f-9747-97213ed085b9\/b64u-MTc0OTMyNDM5NC1iMTFiMTg4Yjk2NWNlMWE2ZGMzYWM2MmFlM2UyYTk4Ni0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b37a58f19046ff42c912e73fc80aeef4c9190bc9845a95496e471f09fd55fa09\"><p><\/p><p><\/p><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/3d-model-generator-from-photo">
							Generate a 3D model from a photo with Photo AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Generate a 3D model from a photo with Photo AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want to turn your AI photos into interactive 3D models? With <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq5\">Photo AI<\/a>, you can now generate 3D representations of your photos in just one click: perfect for creators, game devs, or digital product visualization.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/0197c7d8-bfc7-730c-a24b-991151767f9d\/b64u-M2RmYXEud2VicA.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/0197c7d8-bfc7-730c-a24b-991151767f9d\/b64u-M2RmYXEud2VicA.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=f30416689dca11ceeab86bfa889ad29f11016288e5d054b9b1fea2c95ca684d5\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"3dfaq.webp\"><p>One note: 3d model generation isn\u2019t great yet. We use the latest and best models on the market but the quality of especially people isn\u2019t great yet. But we want to offer the feature anwyay.<\/p><p>Here\u2019s how to do it:<\/p><h2 id=\"qfq0iwmd4bt\" data-toc-id=\"qfq0iwmd4bt\">Step 1: Create or select your AI model<\/h2><p>Go to [ Create new AI model ] in the sidebar. Upload around 20 photos of your model: this could be yourself or someone you\u2019ve hired.<\/p><p>In about a minute, Photo AI will train a photorealistic, personalized AI model that looks just like them.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b83-ef3d-7465-8119-c8e5a3f123c7\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.40.30.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b83-ef3d-7465-8119-c8e5a3f123c7\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=3b1bae5d5d52641b726ec7401bcc1cf62f2940015d4cbacc476ed7f3ad4ef119\"><p>You can reuse this model to take AI photos and videos.<\/p><h2 id=\"y8zyqfpxo85\" data-toc-id=\"y8zyqfpxo85\">Step 2: Generate a photo<\/h2><p class=\"p3\">Write a prompt to create a high-quality image of your model. Write an angle and outfit that suits your use case.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b9c-2eab-7596-abf4-c2bd525ec43b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMTYuMzcucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.16.37.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b9c-2eab-7596-abf4-c2bd525ec43b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMTYuMzcucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=9d75f4d1eaaaa574c26aaa7519d0b84a4a68ab31d0f027efc6fc3889926a3d97\"><p class=\"p3\">Or use any of the 100s of photo packs below (under Photo packs):<\/p><h3 id=\"s27iztzrfiy\" data-toc-id=\"s27iztzrfiy\"><strong>\ud83d\udd25 Popular Packs<\/strong><\/h3><ul><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/tinder?ref=faq1\"><strong>Tinder<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Eye-catching dating profile pics with great poses and vibrant colors to help you get more matches<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/hinge?ref=faq1\"><strong>Hinge<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 More natural, candid moments to reflect personality and spark real conversations<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/luxury-lifestyle?ref=faq1\"><strong>Luxury Lifestyle<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 You in Dubai penthouses, yachts, and private jets. Opulence everywhere<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/old-money?ref=faq1\"><strong>Old Money<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Ivy League tennis clubs, polo outfits, and timeless rich-kid energy<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/instagram?ref=faq1\"><strong>Instagram<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Influencer-ready content with lighting and vibe tailored to maximize likes<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h3 id=\"tlmbxsd3ok6\" data-toc-id=\"tlmbxsd3ok6\"><strong>\ud83e\uddd1\u200d\ud83d\udcbc Professional Packs<\/strong><\/h3><ul><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/linkedin-headshots?ref=faq1\"><strong>LinkedIn Headshots<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Studio-quality portraits with neutral backgrounds and sharp lighting<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/startup-founder?ref=faq1\"><strong>Startup Founder Headshots<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Bold, modern photos for pitch decks, websites, or investor decks<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/ceo-headshots?ref=faq1\"><strong>CEO Headshots<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Strong, formal looks for media, board meetings, and executive branding<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h3 id=\"kkrp4wrpx4x\" data-toc-id=\"kkrp4wrpx4x\"><strong>\ud83c\udfad Creative &amp; Fun Packs<\/strong><\/h3><ul><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/1950s-film-noir?ref=faq1\"><strong>1950s Film Noir<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Black and white drama shots with classic Hollywood lighting<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/santorini-summer?ref=faq1\"><strong>Santorini Summer<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 You in Mediterranean paradise, bathed in Greek island light<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/cosplay?ref=faq1\"><strong>Cosplay<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Transform into your favorite characters with cinematic flair<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\"><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/bali-influencer?ref=faq1\"><strong>Bali Influencer<\/strong><\/a> \u2013 Pool villas, tropical vibes, and that Canggu aesthetic<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>You can browse and run photo packs any time after your model is ready. Each shoot takes just seconds and generates a full set of high-resolution, lifelike images that look like you hired a pro photographer.<\/p><h2 id=\"r70ilpfbkbk\" data-toc-id=\"r70ilpfbkbk\"><strong>Step 3: Make the 3D model<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\">Hover over the photo you want to convert, then click <strong>[ Make 3D model ]<\/strong>. The AI will process the image and generate a rotatable 3D mesh that approximates the subject in the photo.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b9c-cc86-7970-889b-9cca506b6b8b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMTcuMjYucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.17.26.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b9c-cc86-7970-889b-9cca506b6b8b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMTcuMjYucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=4388a4481a73be18ae2c6250d29c478047fb11a08f68abe99bf7afb060289dd3\"><p>It will now take a few minutes to generate a 3d model, and then voila!<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974ba4-4805-71d1-81ea-71a102d5e57f\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMjUuMzEucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.25.31.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974ba4-4805-71d1-81ea-71a102d5e57f\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMjUuMzEucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=6d448654f369b5ced6cdcd73ecc8af34722fa3c15e90d4a8cf3e910dfb44f0f2\"><p>Hover over the pic and click [ View ] to open it in the image viewer, where you can drag around your 3d model:<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGJhNy02NTU4LTdiYTktYWM3YS01ZjRmOWZkNDM2NzIiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDQ3YjllODcyMjcyZjQ1ZDEyZTQzNiIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTMyMDk1Mn0.B1Whm2XbL33e12LKLc-EOXMt-Rb5uvX06A8oTsJl9ik\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.26.17.mp4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGJhNy02NTU4LTdiYTktYWM3YS01ZjRmOWZkNDM2NzIiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ0N2I5ZTg3MjI3MmY0NWQxMmU0MzYiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.-znmX4tT7Nr0uhYy45-r7SiKYVqx9huLAMy4dqin428\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"fq6s5iippts\" data-toc-id=\"fq6s5iippts\">Alternatively: Upload your own images to turn into a video<\/h2><p>With Photo AI you can also upload your own images (like real photos you made) and turn them into a 3d model in a similar way.<\/p><ol><li><p>First go to [ Import into gallery ] and select your image.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b87-074a-7334-9622-90a11e37d0ad\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuNDMuNTAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 15.43.50.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b87-074a-7334-9622-90a11e37d0ad\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuNDMuNTAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=a2beed7c8a82c3cd90499a7ef6244608fd76e6bffe4c126059fa663de918ffe1\"><p><\/p><\/li><li><p>Then once it shows up in the gallery, hover over the image and tap [ Make 3d model ].<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b87-0882-7ef7-929a-95e174874f29\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMzQuMDgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-06 at 21.34.08.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b87-0882-7ef7-929a-95e174874f29\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMzQuMDgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=6c301ddb61378048607d9d76bc32bc0fbb0a674ca8f1c5838cf331fc27888221\"><\/li><\/ol><p>Generating a 3d model takes a few minutes, after it\u2019s done you\u2019ll see this:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b97-1b61-7757-b17e-66b0e9861cdb\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMTAuNTYucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.10.56.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68447b9e872272f45d12e436\/01974b97-1b61-7757-b17e-66b0e9861cdb\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTkuMTAuNTYucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=3d2db905204a88cfedbf1ba89883eb70146ae6adca5b80d00c08de9d2fda750e\"><p>When opening your model you can move around it in the image viewer:<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGI5OC03OGFlLTdlYWUtYTkzMi0xMWI1Y2VmNWJmMzEiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDQ3YjllODcyMjcyZjQ1ZDEyZTQzNiIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTMxOTk3M30.6YzDpRWHpBtnolajXsa87cyujIW5tpY9I9D9ELzWzWI\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 19.11.37.mp4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGI5OC03OGFlLTdlYWUtYTkzMi0xMWI1Y2VmNWJmMzEiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ0N2I5ZTg3MjI3MmY0NWQxMmU0MzYiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.qoZQxMJSv7SOKW9DixAvsl-v6ZBwzeoNkoHLFdwezqk\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><p>If you tap [ Download ] you can download a .GLB file of your model. Which most 3d software accepts.<\/p><h2 id=\"fer3bp7p4k4\" data-toc-id=\"fer3bp7p4k4\">Open your 3d model in AR<\/h2><p>Bonus: If you\u2019re on an iPhone (and some Android phones), and you open the 3d model in the image viewer, there\u2019s also an AR option (the 3d cube button in the bottom right) which lets you put your 3d model in the room with you!<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGI5ZS01NDE3LTc0MmQtYjhhZS03MmEzNzhkNjA1YjkiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDQ3YjllODcyMjcyZjQ1ZDEyZTQzNiIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTMyMDM1N30.pAmwm3eFM5pwpVLDkhihBTS9o76NIgyh1mkUG-7_bNM\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"IMG_3269.MP4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGI5ZS01NDE3LTc0MmQtYjhhZS03MmEzNzhkNjA1YjkiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ0N2I5ZTg3MjI3MmY0NWQxMmU0MzYiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.indvc-oGtTUPcYcoCQks9rh1TKKsrrGTC-du4hS0Llc\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"ezw17kqbw3b\" data-toc-id=\"ezw17kqbw3b\"><strong>Use cases:<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\">\u2705 Virtual 3d fashion try-ons<\/p><p class=\"p3\">\u2705 Gaming avatars or NPCs<\/p><p class=\"p3\">\u2705 Product and character previews<\/p><p class=\"p3\">\u2705 Social content with depth and movement<\/p><p>You don\u2019t need 3D software, rigging knowledge, or photogrammetry. Just generate, click, and get your 3D model.<\/p><p>Try it now with <strong>[ Make 3d model ]<\/strong> inside <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq5\">Photo AI<\/a>.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
