										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/batch-img2img">
							Batch Image-to-Image - Edit Multiple Photos at Once with AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Batch Image-to-Image - Edit Multiple Photos at Once with AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Creating AI-enhanced images just got a major upgrade.<\/p><p class=\"p1\">With <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq12\"><strong>Photo AI<\/strong><\/a><strong>\u2019s new [ Batch remix ] and [ Batch try on ] feature<\/strong>, you can now <strong>upload multiple photos at once<\/strong>, and watch as each photo gets remixed and each garment get worn using your trained AI model. That means you (or your hired model) can appear across dozens of unique, stylized images in one go.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/01977917-66fe-7b06-8a19-8b5b085f0298\/b64u-YmF0Y2hyZW1peC53ZWJw.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"batchremix.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/01977917-66fe-7b06-8a19-8b5b085f0298\/b64u-YmF0Y2hyZW1peC53ZWJw.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=7eb74d08e63f20315d209c083cf35cdea9b781020ace842def9e3e71fc0740d7\"><h2 id=\"r0cy8q5qcqa\" data-toc-id=\"r0cy8q5qcqa\">Step 1: Create or select your AI model<\/h2><p>Go to [ Create new AI model ] in the sidebar. Upload around 20 photos of your model, this could be yourself or someone you\u2019ve hired.<\/p><p>In about a minute, Photo AI will train a photorealistic, personalized AI model that looks just like them.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/019778de-b752-7dd5-b093-306226d8b256\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.40.30.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/019778de-b752-7dd5-b093-306226d8b256\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=a8dfbab3e1b82481935343c72d5fee2ce5a9dfd5469e2b43983ed6fcc219c5ae\"><p>You can reuse this model to try on different outfits endlessly.<\/p><h2 id=\"a14cd8f7xwq\" data-toc-id=\"a14cd8f7xwq\"><strong>Step 2: Go to [ Remix a photo ] in the sidebar<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">This opens the remix panel where you can upload your photos:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/019778f2-df93-7ab0-b66e-d483a4f976b6\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuMzQuMjEucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-16 at 15.34.21.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/019778f2-df93-7ab0-b66e-d483a4f976b6\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuMzQuMjEucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=bc9390f43fb36e8e421368d46468a75fb19f90c51e4c596efd0415cee90d06de\"><h2 id=\"fayyffyd3y2\" data-toc-id=\"fayyffyd3y2\"><strong>Step 3: Upload multiple images<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Upload multiple photos \u2014 your original photo shoots, poses, or inspiration images.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/019778f5-7a62-7274-9e81-0e9863e6b75a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuMzcuMTMucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-16 at 15.37.13.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/019778f5-7a62-7274-9e81-0e9863e6b75a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuMzcuMTMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=986d27dce0d01906f1d196421e3e4bc9dc3a46109bf4a95e2fad9e6161648e42\"><h2 id=\"45w1cd61diy\" data-toc-id=\"45w1cd61diy\"><strong>Step 4: Tap [ Take photo ]<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Each photo gets processed individually with the model applied, producing consistent AI portraits, fashion shots, or product previews.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/019778fa-5a15-7456-b2aa-4bdac827ec95\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuNDEuMjEucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-16 at 15.41.21.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68501715aad2ed2c3d3ff98a\/019778fa-5a15-7456-b2aa-4bdac827ec95\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMTYgYXQgMTUuNDEuMjEucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=438eac6b3098e2974fa554472020527559b1ee9d163bd2abae9c3e23d90db396\"><p><\/p><p class=\"p3\">\ud83d\udc49 Try batch img2img now with [ Remix a photo ] mode on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq12\">Photo AI<\/a>.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/how-to-take-photos-with-multiple-people-in-them">
							How to take photos with multiple people in them?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to take photos with multiple people in them?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>You can use up to 4 different models at the same time on Photo AI:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/69790b2e93610b48e78df4e4\/019c00d5-f431-71f2-9997-c19781750822\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjcgYXQgMTYuMDIuMTkucG5n.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/69790b2e93610b48e78df4e4\/019c00d5-f431-71f2-9997-c19781750822\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjcgYXQgMTYuMDIuMTkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=9c15121afc6dc1e1a2320181ffbc54a84a3e11b0a78f8164b5ffde1a2a73548c\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2026-01-27 at 16.02.19.png\"><p>Just hold [ \u21e7 Shift ] or [ \u2325 Alt ] or long press on a model to add it to your selection. To reset it and select a single model again just click or short press it.<\/p><p>Make sure you toggle \ud83c\udf4c Nano Banana Pro for best results. Hyper Realism m<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
