								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/67707c443dbb299c8af10812\/01974a37-da92-71a8-9d20-654db65204e5\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTIuNDcuMzgucG5n.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/67707c443dbb299c8af10812\/01974a37-da92-71a8-9d20-654db65204e5\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTIuNDcuMzgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=8d17af8f4565d5e6ecdc81b0a1eec2c56b169a6d987e93fac30ee73b7fcd73cc\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 12.47.38.png\"><p>If you sign up for the yearly plan, the pricing is over 50% cheaper, which means 6+ months free compared to regular monthly pricing.<\/p><p>This is our way of thanking you for your trust in our Photo AI and lets us reinvest your money to improve the product.<\/p>",
