							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/i-generated-a-photo-with-nano-banana-pro-but-it-shows-as-hyper-realism-why">
							I generated a photo with Nano Banana Pro but it shows as Hyper Realism, why?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "I generated a photo with Nano Banana Pro but it shows as Hyper Realism, why?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Nano Banana Pro by Google has strict content moderation. If it detects your photo is too suggestive, it rejects the generation. There\u2019s nothing we can do about that.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6971059f6dcd94207893289a\/019be181-453f-7faa-a53b-0a1093b4b17b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjEgYXQgMTcuMDEuMzUucG5n.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6971059f6dcd94207893289a\/019be181-453f-7faa-a53b-0a1093b4b17b\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjYtMDEtMjEgYXQgMTcuMDEuMzUucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=52c460b242f032e2581ca48cdf8fc205889f30c2a8e3d895a1eb2d89a1e88eb1\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2026-01-21 at 17.01.35.png\"><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">When this happens, we automatically fall back to our Hyper Realism model to complete your photo. <\/p><p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">You're only charged the lower Hyper Realism credit rate, not the Nano Banana Pro rate.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/restore-photos-ai">
							Restore old photos with AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Restore old photos with AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want to bring your old, faded, or black-and-white photos back to life? With <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq9\">Photo AI<\/a>, restoring them is as easy as a few clicks \u2014 no editing skills needed. Using the latest state-of-the-art AI models to restore them as accurate as possible.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750bd-363d-792a-a845-526a2678633a\/b64u-cGhvdG9fMjAyNS0wNi0wOCAxOC4yOC4zOS5qcGc.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"photo_2025-06-08 18.28.39.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750bd-363d-792a-a845-526a2678633a\/b64u-cGhvdG9fMjAyNS0wNi0wOCAxOC4yOC4zOS5qcGc.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b3640303068ef31995089f5bc6684f7cf833506fa749db7e90609ff983b1b6d0\"><h2 id=\"t4d0y57ycsk\" data-toc-id=\"t4d0y57ycsk\">Step 1: Import your old photo<\/h2><p>Go to the <strong>Gallery<\/strong> tab in Photo AI and click <strong>[ Import to Gallery ]<\/strong>. Upload your original old or damaged photo. This can be a scan of a printed photo or any image file.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750ab-f7ee-783a-95a4-a95bad7cd789\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTguNTIuMDcucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 18.52.07.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750ab-f7ee-783a-95a4-a95bad7cd789\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTguNTIuMDcucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=6a542837dd260685b62f40288630644817fe245230e02c744e3d5dcd8fbc03f9\"><h2 id=\"5f2olxsxyy7\" data-toc-id=\"5f2olxsxyy7\">Step 2: Click [ Magic Edit ]<\/h2><p>Once uploaded, hover over the photo and click the <strong>[ Magic Edit ]<\/strong> button. A popup will appear where you can enter an instruction.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750ac-4d0a-70ce-a992-049f0cd17f5a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTguNTIuMzAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 18.52.30.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750ac-4d0a-70ce-a992-049f0cd17f5a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTguNTIuMzAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=692feeb6decc84a512f31f28501f998e9af5976cff265083c3ecac4d00961c7e\"><h2 id=\"4sc647ms0pa\" data-toc-id=\"4sc647ms0pa\">Step 3: Type your restoration prompt<\/h2><p>In the input field, type \u201crestore old photo in color\u201d and press Continue.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750ac-d826-730a-9372-f063a7c751c7\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTguNTMuMDIucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 18.53.02.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750ac-d826-730a-9372-f063a7c751c7\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTguNTMuMDIucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b6e53043ac44665a9ab407fef9f69c2dac709a4a622e392a5887088ecaffc506\"><h2 id=\"5y7s0ya72r2\" data-toc-id=\"5y7s0ya72r2\">Step 4: Enjoy your restored photo<\/h2><p>Within about 10 seconds, your restored and colorized photo will appear. You can download it, share it, or keep editing with more prompts.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750b4-b536-73ab-b475-210fe60b1600\/b64u-WFozUUc4UGxFQ0t2emVjVHdzX0NzX2VjNTI0OWM5NTllNzQ1OGRiMmE3ZGRmNmRiMWEzMzJjLmpwZw.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"XZ3QG8PlECKvzecTws_Cs_ec5249c959e7458db2a7ddf6db1a332c.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845cca77868022caa8af80d\/019750b4-b536-73ab-b475-210fe60b1600\/b64u-WFozUUc4UGxFQ0t2emVjVHdzX0NzX2VjNTI0OWM5NTllNzQ1OGRiMmE3ZGRmNmRiMWEzMzJjLmpwZw.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=febc7f781bb07f55e22c8e6f0927acafbd7d42118bf34a46b13e5b43426fc954\"><h2 id=\"oxp6t8erfsk\" data-toc-id=\"oxp6t8erfsk\">Step 5 (optional): Make more edits<\/h2><p>In some cases the AI will make mistakes. Like the cobblestone street turns into grass. In those cases try doing it again with \u201crestore old photo in color but keep the streets cobblestone\u201d and it usually works.<\/p><h2 id=\"lqqdi87pp0p\" data-toc-id=\"lqqdi87pp0p\">Step 6: Turn your old photo into a video<\/h2><p>Once you have a clear photo, you can turn it into a real-life video too. Just hover over the photo and tap [ Make video ] and write a prompt. Here I wrote \u201cman turns and looks into camera\u201d.<\/p><p>A few minutes later you\u2019ll see your video. It\u2019s as if you take a little peak into history and turning it alive!<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NTBiOC03MGVhLTcwOWItODhjMi1iNzk0MGVkOGY4ZDYiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDVjY2E3Nzg2ODAyMmNhYThhZjgwZCIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTQwNTk1NX0.YbLo1wdiQKqmN8mIhhPcgjXRRqazajL06M_IZMjtYmU\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NTBiOC03MGVhLTcwOWItODhjMi1iNzk0MGVkOGY4ZDYiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ1Y2NhNzc4NjgwMjJjYWE4YWY4MGQiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.TSvZCDX5EUedmu6eRGsg5QLpFrO1-1t-JXjhuQ_U3SM\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"qtoo4k53z7w\" data-toc-id=\"qtoo4k53z7w\">Take aways<\/h2><p>Photo AI makes high-quality photo restoration instant, automated, and accessible \u2014 no Photoshop needed.<\/p><p>Start restoring photos now on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq9\">Photo AI<\/a>!<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/talking-ai-video-generator">
							How to create talking AI videos with Photo AI?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to create talking AI videos with Photo AI?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>You can now create talking AI videos with Photo AI.<\/p><img src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/0194ecff-6fc3-7ca0-bf2d-f031752d36ed.png\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><p>You first take an AI photo and then if you like the look of one, hover over the photo and tap [ Make video ]. It will then process for a few minutes and turn your AI photo into a lifelike moving AI video, like below.<\/p><p>Tip: if you want to make your video look sharper, first [ Upscale ] it before making a video. <\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/0194ed00-9118-70bc-8e40-fbf347aa6d28.mp4\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><\/video><p>You can try a few times, and then when you have a video that you like the look of, again hover over it and tap [ Make talking video ].<\/p><p>A popup will show up to enter the script you want your AI model to speak.<\/p><img src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/0194ed02-8beb-7e24-b813-91c86309f444.png\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><p>It will then start processing and after a few minutes, your talking AI video will show up in your gallery like this:<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/0194ed05-e3ea-7d65-8ace-3a87a010c760.mp4\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><\/video><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/report-bugs">
							How do I report a bug or request a new feature?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How do I report a bug or request a new feature?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>To report a bug, go to our <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/ideasandbugs.com\/?b=664b949974fca5a6a66f8058\">bug board<\/a> and press [ Create new post ].<\/p><p>Make sure you use the SAME email as on your Photo AI account when reporting a bug.<\/p><p>Usually bugs reported are fixed within hours. While feature requests if accepted might take a few days or weeks.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"right\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/684596d78de31ad58edb04d9\/01974fd5-c239-7576-acb3-3ccdf9e46ec9\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuNTguMTQucG5n.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/684596d78de31ad58edb04d9\/01974fd5-c239-7576-acb3-3ccdf9e46ec9\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuNTguMTQucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=9b325dc4be45ecde28e5c8c031c8043c57824eb0095e0ded152a9f1dcffd478c\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 14.58.14.png\"><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/ai-thumbnail-tool">
							How to create AI Thumbnails for YouTube with Photo AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to create AI Thumbnails for YouTube with Photo AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want MrBeast-style thumbnails without hiring a designer? With <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq17\">Photo AI<\/a>, you can generate custom YouTube thumbnails in minutes featuring yourself anywhere using AI.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6f9-a63b-7534-a56a-fa1c79ab83d1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMzcuNDIud2VicA.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.37.42.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6f9-a63b-7534-a56a-fa1c79ab83d1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMzcuNDIud2VicA.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=94941a8796e45fa85ccddad680d2e9230e654542f22d4950777b72d914d444ce\"><h2 id=\"8qs5ftxxsf4\" data-toc-id=\"8qs5ftxxsf4\">\ud83e\udde0 Step 1: Create or Select your model<\/h2><p>Start by select an existing one you\u2019ve already made:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6db-9b05-7170-acb2-e6a6b693fea1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMDUuMjkucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.05.29.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6db-9b05-7170-acb2-e6a6b693fea1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMDUuMjkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=74a3e522dd2bbe2cca8d45d5c8e7cf49d7d04298f1be16aed424af99ea22fd5a\"><p>Or create a new model first:<\/p><p>Go to [ Create new AI model ] in the sidebar. Upload around 20 photos of your model, this could be yourself or someone you\u2019ve hired.<\/p><p>In about a minute, Photo AI will train a photorealistic, personalized AI model that looks just like them.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6db-2ff1-7c61-9392-873fd13e909a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.40.30.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6db-2ff1-7c61-9392-873fd13e909a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=0122cf06a60e3014035fd82ce10853dff519503c5d6df412dfd55d0caff6a398\"><p>You can reuse this model for photos in the future.<\/p><h2 id=\"z1i16eawse2\" data-toc-id=\"z1i16eawse2\">\ud83d\uddc2 Step 2: Open the \u201cPhoto Packs\u201d Tab<\/h2><p>Scroll down and click on the <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/ai-thumbnail-tool\">AI Thumbnail Tool<\/a> photo pack. This is pre-optimized for bold facial expressions and high-conversion poses perfect for YouTube.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6dd-84e3-7064-b01d-9d0a14ee5364\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMDcuMjMucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.07.23.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6dd-84e3-7064-b01d-9d0a14ee5364\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMDcuMjMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=18b6b2712feec6260ac6d928a7d3d5455efcb8a08f37f4843ea7a5a7bd28107a\"><p>Tap the photo pack and confirm:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6dd-c2b9-7966-b12b-97f6750c04ad\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMDcuNDYucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.07.46.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6dd-c2b9-7966-b12b-97f6750c04ad\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMDcuNDYucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=8742db525e49ec5b61d41a30cb43f6e03c7106da369e909fa2cf88dc0127ce79\"><p>It will now start running the photo pack and generating AI thumbnails. Once it\u2019s done it\u2019ll look like this:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6de-b464-7117-bee4-fd6affd91e25\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMDguNTAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.08.50.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6de-b464-7117-bee4-fd6affd91e25\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMDguNTAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=e1f791a3d6d039bee0f174c0cbdffc23c5ddfc394a57cbec267e3b2af8f3b50c\"><p>On purpose most images have bright colorful backgrounds that are easy to remove. Just this color as a background doesn\u2019t make the thumbnail very interesting though.<\/p><h2 id=\"5i4qbzqzozx\" data-toc-id=\"5i4qbzqzozx\">\u270f\ufe0f Step 3: Edit Background with [ Magic Edit ]<\/h2><p>Pick a photo you like, maybe upscale it:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e1-0a97-73d4-b1d1-652c1e129c20\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMTEuMDgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.11.08.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e1-0a97-73d4-b1d1-652c1e129c20\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMTEuMDgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=7ae4f0d5e08cabd123aeee5d03b12f191ec04aa48843082302830cf4a0220872\"><p>Then hover over it, and tap [ Magic Edit ]:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e1-3c63-7058-848b-6d7a94fa04d6\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMTEuMTYucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.11.16.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e1-3c63-7058-848b-6d7a94fa04d6\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMTEuMTYucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=492b7a693afcbbc2969d7e284d6d050c14f35a6fc2535f95784fbeb7aa62e42f\"><p>Now type what you want to see for your thumbnail:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e2-324f-751b-9f1b-8db7dce85886\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMTIuNDEucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.12.41.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e2-324f-751b-9f1b-8db7dce85886\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMTIuNDEucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=ab3a74f063d3b5633c9da1bf7798a188f8ad2f93a346e7b4b6d38742a2494926\"><p><strong>Examples:<\/strong><\/p><p>\u201cchange background to a green swamp in a horror movie\u201d<\/p><p>or<\/p><p>\u201cadd a giant treasure chest with golden coins behind me\u201d<\/p><p>or<\/p><p>\u201cchange to uninhabited tropical island with coconut trees\u201d<\/p><h2 id=\"4k6cfpz2eey\" data-toc-id=\"4k6cfpz2eey\">\u2705 Step 4: Done!<\/h2><p>Your thumbnail is ready to go:<\/p><p>\u201cchange background to a green swamp in a horror movie\u201d<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e2-b9ef-70fe-80ca-ecba04fbc319\/b64u-MTc1MTExNzk4MS0zYjU4ZDVmNWY1NDc2NDQzY2JhOTc0ZTAyMzU3NzViYi0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1751117981-3b58d5f5f5476443cba974e0235775bb-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e2-b9ef-70fe-80ca-ecba04fbc319\/b64u-MTc1MTExNzk4MS0zYjU4ZDVmNWY1NDc2NDQzY2JhOTc0ZTAyMzU3NzViYi0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=21af063fb724a39784267c6f99fb6945e0c8fbb2ba072393bc77bb1dcdf0cd1c\"><p>\u201cadd a giant treasure chest with golden coins behind me\u201d<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e4-3472-772d-9ee4-6a16620d920e\/b64u-MTc1MTEyMDA3NC01ZDBmOGMxMWMzYTNlMzhlZmYzOWM1N2NkMjc0ZjIyOS0xLmpwZWc.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1751120074-5d0f8c11c3a3e38eff39c57cd274f229-1.jpeg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e4-3472-772d-9ee4-6a16620d920e\/b64u-MTc1MTEyMDA3NC01ZDBmOGMxMWMzYTNlMzhlZmYzOWM1N2NkMjc0ZjIyOS0xLmpwZWc.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=108acfdc4d46fb5ff46a229f4f17d0daf02915a5cbf7dfd8ae24035698b67007\"><p>\u201cchange to uninhabited tropical island with coconut trees\u201d (this one had one Zoom Out before)<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e3-463d-79e8-9bcf-2158e778b0bb\/b64u-MDE5N2I2ZTMtNDVhZS03ZDdmLWJkNDAtMTlkOWZhNjhmNTU5.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197b6e3-45ae-7d7f-bd40-19d9fa68f559\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e3-463d-79e8-9bcf-2158e778b0bb\/b64u-MDE5N2I2ZTMtNDVhZS03ZDdmLWJkNDAtMTlkOWZhNjhmNTU5.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=25a4d4046a49cd366efee3f5002615caf2e641a0a7e6e47ea3984832be382b3e\"><p><strong>Optional:<\/strong> hit [ Upscale ] to boost resolution and get ultra-sharp detail, and [ Zoom out ] to show more of the full body of the model.<\/p><p>It usually takes a few edits and tweaks to get exactly what you want:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e9-d309-7a5a-96f3-4810b82218d1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMjAuNDgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 15.20.48.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b6e9-d309-7a5a-96f3-4810b82218d1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTUuMjAuNDgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=df525bcdbbb5efec0c92cf2c7e92f242f1f17767fe37d4a431be7bc76a1321fa\"><p>And here\u2019s how it looks on YouTube:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"Image\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b744-06d9-7c6e-a738-897e5c252ad0\/b64u-MDE5N2I3NDQtMDZhYi03MTE2LTgyZTgtNTkxYWQzN2I2MzM0.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197b744-06ab-7116-82e8-591ad37b6334\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685ff642348159fc27595c21\/0197b744-06d9-7c6e-a738-897e5c252ad0\/b64u-MDE5N2I3NDQtMDZhYi03MTE2LTgyZTgtNTkxYWQzN2I2MzM0.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=72df1705cf858b5084ad857349747456f60915b947a66192e925eb1701dc73c4\"><p><\/p><p>No Photoshop, no designers \u2014 just viral thumbnails, instantly.<\/p><p>Try it now on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq17\">Photo AI<\/a>.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/how-to-make-ai-influencer">
							How to make AI influencers with Photo AI?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to make AI influencers with Photo AI?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">Yes, Photo AI has a dedicated feature to create AI influencers from scratch now!<\/span><\/p><img src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/0194f14e-2233-73af-b9d5-2518178b4855.jpg\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><p>The AI influencer above was created with Photo AI in less than 30 seconds<\/p><p><strong>AI influencer: <\/strong>25-year old Spanish model Erica with brown eyes and straightened long blonde hair<\/p><p><strong>Prompt<\/strong>: \u201cfront view of model wearing a strapless black top and a delicate necklace. the model is smiling and positioned in front of a lush green bush adorned with red and white flowers. in the background, there is a lit-up eiffel tower and a classic lamp post against a clear evening sky.\u201d<\/p><h1 id=\"i76z5mxttim\" data-toc-id=\"i76z5mxttim\">Create your first AI influencer<\/h1><p>Simply login to Photo AI and in the sidebar scroll down to [ Create new AI model ] and select [ Create a new AI influencer ].<\/p><p>Instead of uploading photos like you\u2019d normally do to create an AI model, it will now ask you to design your AI influencer from scratch.<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/0194f0c2-8fa9-7394-92b4-0494a5e4034f.mp4\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><\/video><p>While designing your AI influencer you will see a quick preview of how they will look so you can adjust accordingly. The preview is low quality (but quick) and your final AI influencer will look much better of course:<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/0194f0c4-31c6-70ca-9f8f-08946fcaa7e2.mp4\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><\/video><p>Creating an AI influencer is fast and within half a minute it\u2019ll be done and Photo AI will have created some sample photos like it does for every model, like headshots and Instagram photos like.<\/p><p>Once created, you can take photos, generate videos, and even make your AI influencer talk, which gives you a lot of opportunities to create viral content for your AI influencer. And you might be able to monetize that too on social media platforms.<\/p><p>AI influencers can be monetized through product placements or selling their content directly.<\/p><p>AI influencers are quite a recent development but they already make money and it doesn\u2019t look like it\u2019ll stop to grow as a new industry soon. For example, Spanish AI influencer Lil Miquela makes $10 million per year, German AI fashion model Noonoouri makes $500,000 per year, and South African AI supermodel Shudu makes $2,000 per sponsored post.<\/p><img src=\"https:\/\/fb-usercontent.fra1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com\/0194ec2a-fd5d-785f-be0c-24d8ad5dd8ab.png\" data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\"><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/virtual-try-on-for-e-commerce">
							Generate virtual try ons on with real models: boost your e-commerce store with Photo AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Generate virtual try ons on with real models: boost your e-commerce store with Photo AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want to showcase clothes on real-looking models without expensive photo shoots? <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq4\">Photo AI<\/a> makes it easy to virtually try on clothes using AI-generated photos and videos. Perfect for e-commerce stores, fashion designers, or Shopify sellers.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/0197c7b0-8135-776a-8da9-83928f2f4f9e\/b64u-dHJ5b25mYXEgKDEpLndlYnA.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/0197c7b0-8135-776a-8da9-83928f2f4f9e\/b64u-dHJ5b25mYXEgKDEpLndlYnA.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=16d591d992872e1493ac53e1c9b22e873c999a39ef540dfd286349d2b77f10d0\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"tryonfaq (1).webp\"><p>Here\u2019s how to use the Virtual Try On Clothes feature on Photo AI:<\/p><h2 id=\"qfq0iwmd4bt\" data-toc-id=\"qfq0iwmd4bt\">Step 1: Create or select your AI model<\/h2><p>Go to [ Create new AI model ] in the sidebar. Upload around 20 photos of your model, this could be yourself or someone you\u2019ve hired.<\/p><p>In about a minute, Photo AI will train a photorealistic, personalized AI model that looks just like them.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b44-130b-7d04-8bfa-7780a46e81f2\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.40.30.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b44-130b-7d04-8bfa-7780a46e81f2\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=ecbee7567cf302e0370d7574dc34a69264c73d61c9494b0f4fa0cacd8f2a004c\"><p>You can reuse this model to try on different outfits endlessly.<\/p><h2 id=\"k5l1qp34mfc\" data-toc-id=\"k5l1qp34mfc\">Step 2: Open the Try-On tool<\/h2><p>Click [ Try on clothes ] in the sidebar to launch the virtual try-on interface.<\/p><p>Upload a photo of the outfit you want the model to wear. It can be a real garment photo, mockup, or even a designer sketch.<\/p><p>Make sure to select full body, upper body or lower body depending what kind of garment it is.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b47-b7b4-7e3a-8169-97042d4195a4\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDQuMjgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.44.28.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b47-b7b4-7e3a-8169-97042d4195a4\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDQuMjgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=acd607bb668f9ad2e55bcc8a98891b133d7ca0ee830635aa1fb2a9ff68bf7842\"><h2 id=\"88qb5iqf3qk\" data-toc-id=\"88qb5iqf3qk\">Step 3: Take the photo<\/h2><p>Select your trained model and click [ Take photo ]. The AI will generate a realistic image of that person wearing the outfit, perfect for product pages, lookbooks, or social posts.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b48-4ee4-73d2-8aa0-3bbb9903a208\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDQuMDkucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.44.09.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b48-4ee4-73d2-8aa0-3bbb9903a208\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDQuMDkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=5de2bcc314c34a48ede7ba1330cc4e73d9f85e63677287f19cbf75e45261d7be\"><h2 id=\"bxdi7w7plmr\" data-toc-id=\"bxdi7w7plmr\">Step 4 (optional): Change the setting<\/h2><p>You can change the setting of your model in your prompt. But if you\u2019ve already taken a nice photo and would like to change it then you can! Just hover over your photo and tap [ Relight ]. Then write where you want to place the model. For example \u201ca beach in Thailand\u201d:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b4b-d3f4-7a39-ac91-aca1d07a03c3\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDguNTcucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.48.57.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b4b-d3f4-7a39-ac91-aca1d07a03c3\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDguNTcucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=7566ff2df9fd2c0973a68792fd173b5e2cce69d19dac6109a1f9e6fde8a878d9\"><p>Wait a little bit and voila, she\u2019s on a Thai beach:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b60-799b-7994-b6c1-9566bd0b9cc5\/b64u-MTc0OTMxNjEwNy00Zjg2MmFjZDNlOWEyZDU3ODcyZDM1MGI5OWU1NzZmOC0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749316107-4f862acd3e9a2d57872d350b99e576f8-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b60-799b-7994-b6c1-9566bd0b9cc5\/b64u-MTc0OTMxNjEwNy00Zjg2MmFjZDNlOWEyZDU3ODcyZDM1MGI5OWU1NzZmOC0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=48be1689e146841591de24c2b6b944db761217c3742efc79f643f860b673f205\"><h2 id=\"z6dbb7t5b6q\" data-toc-id=\"z6dbb7t5b6q\">Step 5 (optional): Make a video<\/h2><p>Hover over the photo and click [ Make video ] to animate the outfit in motion, no camera crew or travel required anymore!<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b65-3547-78de-acb1-32923aecff7f\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTguMTYuMzUucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 18.16.35.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68446a1108f3208f136b851c\/01974b65-3547-78de-acb1-32923aecff7f\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTguMTYuMzUucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=bde651f204c90660b23a9258ca264c80d26555035b8d789fa06dbece6f660a78\"><p>Wait a bit and then:<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGI2OS02ZTgzLTcyNjEtYmIyYS0xYzMyZmU5Mzk1NzgiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDQ2YTExMDhmMzIwOGYxMzZiODUxYyIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTMxNjg5MH0.g1iCvu5VJlRZ4CWh4M2LiWf_8cV2v-KlX8RirM1hkBE\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"final_output (8).mp4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGI2OS02ZTgzLTcyNjEtYmIyYS0xYzMyZmU5Mzk1NzgiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ0NmExMTA4ZjMyMDhmMTM2Yjg1MWMiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.z2NHYWa4svNCEp8e_rdrQTH-QyqBS4hHsLm_UPEulV0\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><p>And inside your store:<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGI3My1lZjNiLTc0MDEtYWZmNC1lOGIzZWU5NDJhZWIiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDQ2YTExMDhmMzIwOGYxMzZiODUxYyIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTMxNzU3OH0.vDyilqseeTliSqQEelGaggU4hnJidBwNe7J7Nl5MQlg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 18.26.41-converted.mp4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NGI3My1lZjNiLTc0MDEtYWZmNC1lOGIzZWU5NDJhZWIiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ0NmExMTA4ZjMyMDhmMTM2Yjg1MWMiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.iq65xraGqoNnFqYxy5UenHWYjplBd7bMynX6kXN9HQU\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"x630xil8rm3\" data-toc-id=\"x630xil8rm3\">Why it\u2019s powerful:<\/h2><p>\u2705 Use real models (yourself or hired), no deepfake, no stock<\/p><p>\u2705 Showcase clothes before manufacturing<\/p><p>\u2705 Great for Shopify stores, independent designers, and fashion startups<\/p><p>\u2705 Instantly generate lifestyle content, product photos, and even videos<\/p><p>\u2705 Do photo shoots anywhere in the world without a photographer<\/p><p>\u2705 Do video shoots anywhere in the world without a camera crew and traveling<\/p><p>Try it now on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq4\">Photo AI<\/a>, sign up and then go to [ Try on clothes ] and bring your fashion to life without ever picking up a camera.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/ai-commercial-use-license">
							Can I use Photo AI photos commercially?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Can I use Photo AI photos commercially?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Yes, the Pro, Max and Ultra plans give you a commercial use license.<\/p><p>The Starter plan is only for personal use.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/what-payment-methods-do-you-accept">
							What payment methods do you accept?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "What payment methods do you accept?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>We accept payments via credit or debit cards, including MasterCard, VISA, American Express, as well as iDeal, SOFORT, Bancontact, Przelewy24, Giropay, EPS, GrabPay, AliPay, and many more. <\/p><p>However, we do not accept PayPal or cryptocurrency and are not planning to right now.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/anti-ai-geoguessr">
							How to avoid getting d0xed with AI GeoGuessr by using Photo AI's Anti-AI GeoGuessr						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to avoid getting d0xed with AI GeoGuessr by using Photo AI's Anti-AI GeoGuessr",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>AI GeoGuessr tools are getting eerily good, they can now guess where you live just from a glimpse outside your window:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"GeoSpy AI can find your exact location from even an indoor photo\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b68e-5533-7e7e-83c6-834f89c6c3e9\/b64u-MDE5N2I2OGUtNTRjZC03YTI1LTkwZjItMjAzNTdkOTc0NTEw.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197b68e-54cd-7a25-90f2-20357d974510\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b68e-5533-7e7e-83c6-834f89c6c3e9\/b64u-MDE5N2I2OGUtNTRjZC03YTI1LTkwZjItMjAzNTdkOTc0NTEw.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=6effa1bea3b71fded5f060a654434955483aef6e92da10378fb290772b37bf56\"><p>Matching that window view with Google Street View finds your exact location:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"GeoSpy AI can find your exact location from even an indoor photo - 2\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b68e-8796-7204-97d3-c910ad1c5e8b\/b64u-MDE5N2I2OGUtODc2OS03ZDhlLTg5NTItN2IxOTdkYmUwMTc4.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197b68e-8769-7d8e-8952-7b197dbe0178\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b68e-8796-7204-97d3-c910ad1c5e8b\/b64u-MDE5N2I2OGUtODc2OS03ZDhlLTg5NTItN2IxOTdkYmUwMTc4.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=fd61f8d4b94fc6be9add45660c87f6beb42c6d7b3b802c7b249ee642bc9d063a\"><p>To keep you private, we built you a simple solution with <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq16\">Photo AI<\/a>.<\/p><h2 id=\"kdd0wocmtz4\" data-toc-id=\"kdd0wocmtz4\"><strong>Here\u2019s how to protect your location online:<\/strong><\/h2><h2 id=\"z0kob2poc1x\" data-toc-id=\"z0kob2poc1x\"><strong>1. Upload your photo<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p2\">Pick a photo (or selfie) at home with a window in the background showing your city:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b68f-f337-7dd8-97f0-c717e3d1a5bb\/b64u-MDE5N2I2OGYtZjI3Ny03NmNjLTliZDgtYWZlOGRhYzc4NTYz.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197b68f-f277-76cc-9bd8-afe8dac78563\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b68f-f337-7dd8-97f0-c717e3d1a5bb\/b64u-MDE5N2I2OGYtZjI3Ny03NmNjLTliZDgtYWZlOGRhYzc4NTYz.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=6c5299cfc50c2772b207ca3ec36c00992cfe92bfaeda13c59b91bc2ee6e96b07\"><p>Then upload it into Photo AI using [ Import into gallery ]:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b694-0617-7808-83f4-b9a345239f1d\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTMuNDcuMTMucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 13.47.13.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b694-0617-7808-83f4-b9a345239f1d\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTMuNDcuMTMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=a07ddb91c5f223f9875b5d512a1200aa16f4537f8c87595aeb498bc4475a41cd\"><h2 id=\"f2sbsswzmz3\" data-toc-id=\"f2sbsswzmz3\"><strong>2. Edit your photo with AI<\/strong><\/h2><p>Hover over your imported photo and press [ Magic Edit ]<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b692-c7da-7e15-88ab-54bd0dcc444a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTMuNDUuNTMucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 13.45.53.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b692-c7da-7e15-88ab-54bd0dcc444a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTMuNDUuNTMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=427ecdc7dad166e991adc91d27063760ee8f858ca2a380819f4fa38efbd63309\"><p class=\"p2\">A prompt popup will appear.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b692-6dfb-7cec-b132-7949cd3d557d\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTMuNDUuMjAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-28 at 13.45.20.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b692-6dfb-7cec-b132-7949cd3d557d\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjggYXQgMTMuNDUuMjAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=85c2bfdd5770693359e0420e3857b4804fc4f139b6b9b4bbf7921966828f1242\"><p class=\"p2\">\"Change window view to Bangkok skyscraper at 40th floor\"<\/p><p class=\"p3\">or<\/p><p class=\"p2\">\"Change the window view to a chalet in the Swiss alps\"<\/p><p class=\"p2\">Press Enter.<\/p><p class=\"p2\">Photo AI will regenerate the photo with the new background.<\/p><h2 id=\"iq8ektcs02d\" data-toc-id=\"iq8ektcs02d\"><strong>3. Done!<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p1\">Now, the view outside your window is no longer real \u2014 and no AI detective can tell where you live.<\/p><p class=\"p1\">Here\u2019s it in Bangkok on the 40th floor of a skyscraper:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b694-be08-71ed-94b3-b020c574cd88\/b64u-MTc1MTExNDcxMy1kNDU1ZWQzY2Y3ZDA5ZmIwYjY0YjgzOTFlZjU4ZTc4ZC0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1751114713-d455ed3cf7d09fb0b64b8391ef58e78d-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b694-be08-71ed-94b3-b020c574cd88\/b64u-MTc1MTExNDcxMy1kNDU1ZWQzY2Y3ZDA5ZmIwYjY0YjgzOTFlZjU4ZTc4ZC0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=fa4bb3bdd949580dd8215007dc058572eefe7d0d8a123e890e85882b90745e65\"><p class=\"p4\">And here it is in a Swiss mountain village:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b695-82ab-749f-9da2-6c87846dff36\/b64u-MTc1MTExNDcxNC1mMzIzOTk4MDcxZTNhYTUyZTU2MzhlNGY5N2FmYTJhMS0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1751114714-f323998071e3aa52e5638e4f97afa2a1-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685fe15bf83519ea1544beff\/0197b695-82ab-749f-9da2-6c87846dff36\/b64u-MTc1MTExNDcxNC1mMzIzOTk4MDcxZTNhYTUyZTU2MzhlNGY5N2FmYTJhMS0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=6f73d4bf110d42601a94a6524c10a3674481e5bbbd7f5092ab4cc4a5777993fd\"><p class=\"p4\">\ud83d\udd12 <strong>Keep your location private. Let AI work for you, not against you.<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"p1\">Try it now on <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq16\">Photo AI<\/a>.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
