										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/get-more-matches-tinder-photos">
							Tutorial for Tinder, Hinge & Bumble: How to take better photos and get more matches on dating apps with Photo AI						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Tutorial for Tinder, Hinge & Bumble: How to take better photos and get more matches on dating apps with Photo AI",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Let\u2019s be real: dating apps are brutal. Especially if you\u2019re not 6'2\", white, and looking like a Calvin Klein model. That sucks. But we\u2019re not here to complain \u2014 we\u2019re here to win.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d623-a75d-7d60-a1f2-893609d80a56\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMjUuMTcud2VicA.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-06 at 21.25.17.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d623-a75d-7d60-a1f2-893609d80a56\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMjUuMTcud2VicA.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=88a2dca2565a96128c1d9cd6d4e99b084bb82d15dc35c9bf1ad06a018f4d1f92\"><p>The truth is: most guys have <strong>terrible photos<\/strong>, and that\u2019s the easiest thing to fix. With just a bit of effort, you can completely change how you\u2019re perceived online \u2014 from invisible to dateable.<\/p><h3 id=\"yms4y2dz11o\" data-toc-id=\"yms4y2dz11o\">TLDR if you're lazy:<\/h3><ul><li><p>Use travel photos or scenic backdrops<\/p><\/li><li><p>Learn how to pose in masculine ways<\/p><\/li><li><p>Show different emotions and authenticity<\/p><\/li><li><p>Get a pro to shoot + edit for the <em>female gaze<\/em><\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>Boom. More matches. Easy.<\/p><p>Now let\u2019s break it down.<\/p><h3 id=\"ztw601f3503\" data-toc-id=\"ztw601f3503\">1. <strong>Use Scenic Backdrops<\/strong><\/h3><p>A Hinge study showed that travel photos boost likes by <strong>30%<\/strong>, but barely anyone uses them. Why? Most guys are just lazy or don't think it matters.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d61d-91eb-7a15-a6fe-3f976b06ebd1\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MWQtOTExOS03ZjU4LWI2OWYtYzY1YTI1YTRlYTQz.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197d61d-9119-7f58-b69f-c65a25a4ea43\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d61d-91eb-7a15-a6fe-3f976b06ebd1\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MWQtOTExOS03ZjU4LWI2OWYtYzY1YTI1YTRlYTQz.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=3c805166d67083cdc2ba71829b2e25421eedd30ded3e0c934a9b8ab660a790ea\"><p><strong>Pro Tip:<\/strong> Skip bathroom selfies. Find a rooftop, a park, a cool street, a caf\u00e9. Your background should say: \u201cI have a life worth joining.\u201d<\/p><h3 id=\"zdr00wr5r0r\" data-toc-id=\"zdr00wr5r0r\">2. <strong>Master Masculine Poses<\/strong><\/h3><p>Standing like a sad penguin doesn\u2019t help your case. Good posture, sharp angles, and confident body language make a huge difference.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d61f-5723-75a0-8a5c-8fdea930266f\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MWYtNTY5OC03NDYyLThlODItNzMwZGI3NGRkMTBk.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197d61f-5698-7462-8e82-730db74dd10d\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d61f-5723-75a0-8a5c-8fdea930266f\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MWYtNTY5OC03NDYyLThlODItNzMwZGI3NGRkMTBk.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=0631dde960273b7a6a1d91e6280901b48b0d32ee26ec6e2346ddb5a49a139325\"><p><strong>Pro Tip:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><p>Push your chin slightly forward (jawline pop)<\/p><\/li><li><p>Angle your shoulders<\/p><\/li><li><p>Don\u2019t face the camera straight-on like a mugshot<\/p><\/li><li><p>Try action shots \u2014 adjusting a jacket, walking, leaning on a rail<\/p><\/li><\/ul><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d621-38e1-7138-b815-77e9290cf885\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MjEtMzg4ZS03N2M0LWFiNmItNDliMjc1ZjM1MDYy.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197d621-388e-77c4-ab6b-49b275f35062\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d621-38e1-7138-b815-77e9290cf885\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MjEtMzg4ZS03N2M0LWFiNmItNDliMjc1ZjM1MDYy.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=3501a886ec434a8e6e4720a868321972a86cf50c07ef4af2817a692c32a9ae2f\"><h3 id=\"kr8oxb7zets\" data-toc-id=\"kr8oxb7zets\">3. <strong>Show Authentic Emotion<\/strong><\/h3><p>Deadpan = dead profile. Women are drawn to emotion and vibe, not just looks.<\/p><p><strong>Pro Tip:<\/strong> Mix it up \u2014<\/p><ul><li><p>One smiling with teeth<\/p><\/li><li><p>One candid mid-laugh<\/p><\/li><li><p>One brooding, smirky, looking away<\/p><\/li><li><p>One warm or kind-eyed close-up<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>You\u2019re not a mannequin. Show some life.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d622-5d4d-76e6-89d1-ccccab8b49f8\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MjItNWNkOS03NDZkLWEyYjctZDUxNGUwOTc5MWM0.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197d622-5cd9-746d-a2b7-d514e09791c4\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d622-5d4d-76e6-89d1-ccccab8b49f8\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MjItNWNkOS03NDZkLWEyYjctZDUxNGUwOTc5MWM0.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=2ca92fc96049c11a4cbba2a5988bff654b07347253efe51ebfcdf11110ea6da0\"><h3 id=\"fcasqfa2lei\" data-toc-id=\"fcasqfa2lei\">4. <strong>Get Pro Help (Who Gets It)<\/strong><\/h3><p>This isn\u2019t about hiring a wedding photographer. You need someone who knows how to shoot for dating apps \u2014 ideally someone who understands male presentation <strong>for the female gaze<\/strong>.<\/p><p><strong>Pro Tip:<\/strong> Pay someone who:<\/p><ul><li><p>Shoots with intention (lighting, framing, vibe)<\/p><\/li><li><p>Knows how to <em>edit for apps<\/em> (not over-filtered, just clean + sharp)<\/p><\/li><li><p>Understands how to highlight masculinity subtly<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>Usually photo shoots cost $500 to $2,000 so this might not be for everyone.<\/p><h3 id=\"5frd274zbza\" data-toc-id=\"5frd274zbza\">5. <strong>Avoid These Common Mistakes<\/strong><\/h3><ul><li><p>No group photos \u2014 no one wants to guess who you are<\/p><\/li><li><p>No car selfies, gym mirrors, or bathroom shots<\/p><\/li><li><p>No outdated photos (yes, we can tell)<\/p><\/li><li><p>No sunglasses in every pic<\/p><\/li><li><p>No photos where you're cropped from your ex<\/p><\/li><\/ul><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d624-fc65-71ff-a0f2-851b4cbba42a\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MjQtZmMwMy03MWIzLWI4MDAtMGUxYzc1MmZlNDAw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197d624-fc03-71b3-b800-0e1c752fe400\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d624-fc65-71ff-a0f2-851b4cbba42a\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MjQtZmMwMy03MWIzLWI4MDAtMGUxYzc1MmZlNDAw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=5e8d3f830b53b8053f833b7ecde1be751fd6d57cd1f37e8c285eaa74ac64e958\"><h3 id=\"f2d6tif64s7\" data-toc-id=\"f2d6tif64s7\">6. <strong>Use AI to Create Photorealistic Profile Photos<\/strong><\/h3><p>Don\u2019t have great pics? Don\u2019t want to pay $500 for a shoot? Use <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq25\"><strong>Photo AI<\/strong><\/a> to generate photorealistic dating photos \u2014 custom-tailored to look like <em>you<\/em>, in settings and styles that women swipe on.<\/p><h1 id=\"app83e8pm42\" data-toc-id=\"app83e8pm42\">\u26a0\ufe0f FYI: all the photos you see in this article were taken with Photo AI!<\/h1><p><strong>How to start with <\/strong><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq25\"><strong>Photo AI<\/strong><\/a><strong>:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><p>Sign up for an account<\/p><\/li><li><p>Upload 10-20 selfies (clear, varied expressions) to create an AI model of yourself<\/p><\/li><li><p>Run one of the dating photo packs:<\/p><ul><li><p><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/tinder?ref=faq25\">Tinder<\/a><\/p><\/li><li><p><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/bumble-ai-photos?ref=faq25\">Bumble<\/a><\/p><\/li><li><p><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/hinge-ai-photos?ref=faq25\">Hinge<\/a><\/p><\/li><li><p><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/badoo?ref=faq25\">Badoo<\/a><\/p><\/li><li><p><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/ai-dating-photos?ref=faq25\">AI Dating Photos<\/a><\/p><\/li><li><p><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/dating-headshots?ref=faq25\">Dating Headshots<\/a><\/p><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><p>Or write your own prompts like:<\/p><ul><li><p>\u201cmodel standing on a rooftop at sunset\u201d<\/p><\/li><li><p>\u201cmodel in candid coffee shop moment with soft lighting\u201d<\/p><\/li><li><p>\u201cportrait of model with bokeh background in Paris\u201d<\/p><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><p><a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq25\"><strong>Photo AI<\/strong><\/a> will generate high-res, realistic images that look like pro shoots \u2014 without the awkward posing<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>It\u2019s fast, affordable, and you control the vibe at home. Tons of users have gotten better matches <em>instantly<\/em> just from our photos that reflect confidence, style, and story.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" alt=\"Man in wedding photoshoot. bridal style. wedding style. marriage style. weddi... - #12661776 - Royalty Free - AI Photo &amp; Video Generator\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d625-8120-7796-b5d8-661ae145bffe\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MjUtODBjNi03NjZjLTkwN2UtYmQ2OWIxYjEyNjRk.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"0197d625-80c6-766c-907e-bd69b1b1264d\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6867e8d6208d93e42b54db58\/0197d625-8120-7796-b5d8-661ae145bffe\/b64u-MDE5N2Q2MjUtODBjNi03NjZjLTkwN2UtYmQ2OWIxYjEyNjRk.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=5d83396372a1a836d3806374cc7c5b02fc90050eba2f8ba995d436536c814aca\"><h3 id=\"xx8b7ll7m8l\" data-toc-id=\"xx8b7ll7m8l\">Final Thoughts<\/h3><p>Fix your photos, and your matches go up. Period. We\u2019ve seen guys go from <em>zero<\/em> to <em>hundreds<\/em> of matches just by upgrading their photos. One guy after upgrading his photos got 600+ matches. Real number. And now he averages 3 dates a week.<\/p><p>And if you\u2019re lucky you might end up like the couple above after a few dates!<\/p><p>You\u2019re not ugly. Your photos are just bad!<\/p><p>\ud83d\udd17 Try <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq25\"><strong>Photo AI<\/strong><\/a><strong> now<\/strong><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
