										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/remove-object-from-photo">
							How to remove unwanted objects from AI photos						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to remove unwanted objects from AI photos",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Sometimes your AI-generated photos look great\u2026 except for one annoying object in the background \u2014 maybe a table, a person, or something random that ruins the vibe. With <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq15\">Photo AI<\/a>, removing those is easy.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b279-1f67-7323-813d-787f5431ffbd\/b64u-ZWRpdGZhcS53ZWJw.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"editfaq.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b279-1f67-7323-813d-787f5431ffbd\/b64u-ZWRpdGZhcS53ZWJw.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=14a61a5a9a6087b3faa75a3f10a9e5e6433ea161c7c946f1a150a68aea2507eb\"><h2 id=\"w83b3ckyim4\" data-toc-id=\"w83b3ckyim4\">1. Take a photo or import your own<\/h2><p>You can either take a new photo with Photo AI:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b27b-0ac1-72dc-b106-bfdb7ba55b75\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTguNDEuMjgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-27 at 18.41.28.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b27b-0ac1-72dc-b106-bfdb7ba55b75\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTguNDEuMjgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=0d8e76fd07614af8a2a03ac3f99c78d967767b975d3860215cc1daf99f91be53\"><p>Or import your own photo:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b27a-bca4-7d6b-9c82-bbf29afe1fcc\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTguNDEuMDMucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-27 at 18.41.03.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b27a-bca4-7d6b-9c82-bbf29afe1fcc\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTguNDEuMDMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=cfeca21ca4ec23bd16f11f74d95fce0467b64c64b627b1b17b9ce2b818530001\"><h2 id=\"iwybkl4k2ew\" data-toc-id=\"iwybkl4k2ew\">2. Edit your photo<\/h2><p>Tap and hover on the photo you want to edit:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b274-148d-7b39-8a3e-564f3e071da5\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTUuMzAuMjkucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-27 at 15.30.29.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b274-148d-7b39-8a3e-564f3e071da5\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTUuMzAuMjkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=d70cd14b87632d98395b2673455c7d8eb0d560a82be867a4c06ca5ecc3d9587c\"><p>Now tap [ Magic Edit ]:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b274-c0be-7ec8-8385-3570a8eeb388\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTguMzQuMjEucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-27 at 18.34.21.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b274-c0be-7ec8-8385-3570a8eeb388\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTguMzQuMjEucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=e1dfe4c24a8e9ed71dd67746c76a208f7389c42052a46f4ed70caf57df289a01\"><h2 id=\"dm0y4278s6p\" data-toc-id=\"dm0y4278s6p\">3. Describe what you want to remove<\/h2><p>In the popup, describe what you want to remove. For example: \u201cremove table\u201d in the background remove the text on the wall<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b275-1fac-77af-a869-809ebed8c229\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTUuMzAuMzcucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-27 at 15.30.37.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b275-1fac-77af-a869-809ebed8c229\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMjcgYXQgMTUuMzAuMzcucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=18d349de463282a42c5b0a1a926d7a7630f4b39685ef5b887be1d1f6690bed03\"><p>Hit enter and wait 10\u201320 seconds. Photo AI will automatically edit the photo and show you the result.<\/p><h2 id=\"zr8kt3x5d5s\" data-toc-id=\"zr8kt3x5d5s\">4. Done!<\/h2><p>There is your final photo, without the table!<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b275-653f-7e63-8ede-022d4992c318\/b64u-MTc1MTAzNDY0MS1iODlmYWI4MDViZDRhNDg1NDk5ZTJlMDg4MDIxMGRkNC0xLmpwZWc.jpeg\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1751034641-b89fab805bd4a485499e2e0880210dd4-1.jpeg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/685eab4cf83519ea159bd6ac\/0197b275-653f-7e63-8ede-022d4992c318\/b64u-MTc1MTAzNDY0MS1iODlmYWI4MDViZDRhNDg1NDk5ZTJlMDg4MDIxMGRkNC0xLmpwZWc.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=4d2aad20a7d4ede7fc696aacba46acbf37c2c344f25ae64f454ab32e8e0ee938\"><p>This is perfect for cleaning up your AI shots before posting, especially when you\u2019re working with fashion shoots, product displays, or portraits.<\/p><p>Try [ magic Edit ] now on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq15\">Photo AI<\/a> and make your images clean and distraction-free!<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/upscale-your-ai-photos-and-videos-with-one-click-in-photo-ai">
							Upscale your AI photos and videos with one click in Photo AI
						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Upscale your AI photos and videos with one click in Photo AI\n",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want sharper, crisper, high-resolution photos from your AI shoots? <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq7\">Photo AI<\/a>\u2019s <strong>Upscale<\/strong> feature lets you instantly increase the size and quality of any image or video \u2014 no Photoshop, no tech knowledge.<\/p><p class=\"p1\">Whether you\u2019re printing, posting on social, or using images in your online store, Upscale makes your photos and videos pop.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975037-e059-7c6d-b843-dbac83dc1a4a\/b64u-MTc0OTMwNjYyNy1iNTE5MzIzZDg3ZDY2NDJlNzJkMGFhN2M1ZmNjNmU4ZC00LndlYnA.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749306627-b519323d87d6642e72d0aa7c5fcc6e8d-4.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975037-e059-7c6d-b843-dbac83dc1a4a\/b64u-MTc0OTMwNjYyNy1iNTE5MzIzZDg3ZDY2NDJlNzJkMGFhN2M1ZmNjNmU4ZC00LndlYnA.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=cbccb6ea8ba0648394123551b14deaf236f1d80f573cc07dd9fb634ec14e7013\"><h2 id=\"x0w12bbdqdd\" data-toc-id=\"x0w12bbdqdd\"><strong>What does Upscale do?<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\"><strong>Upscale<\/strong> uses advanced AI to:<\/p><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">Increase the <strong>resolution<\/strong> of your image or video (e.g. 512x512 \u2192 2048x2048)<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Sharpen <strong>details<\/strong> like eyes, skin, hair, and clothing<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Remove blur and fix artifacts<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Preserve the original style and subject<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h2 id=\"tcopey8qkc7\" data-toc-id=\"tcopey8qkc7\"><strong>How to use Upscale in Photo AI<\/strong><\/h2><h2 id=\"o1ps50bilm0\" data-toc-id=\"o1ps50bilm0\">Step 1: Create or select your AI model<\/h2><p>Go to [ Create new AI model ] in the sidebar. Upload around 20 photos of your model, this could be yourself or someone you\u2019ve hired.<\/p><p>In about a minute, Photo AI will train a photorealistic, personalized AI model that looks just like them.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975033-0039-734a-9c9d-4cd28b84f4c1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 17.40.30.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975033-0039-734a-9c9d-4cd28b84f4c1\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTcuNDAuMzAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=ebd5c2e61840eef53fffe0775f7cb48af36a081ec43b14bc989432281ce2af1a\"><p>You can reuse this model.<\/p><h2 id=\"poe24oqqi36\" data-toc-id=\"poe24oqqi36\"><strong>Step 2: Generate photos<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Take photos using the camera or explore preset photo packs \u2014 headshots, dating app pics, fashion, lifestyle, and more.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975033-9d0f-7634-a705-b35a39fa3f21\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuMzIuMTgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 15.32.18.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975033-9d0f-7634-a705-b35a39fa3f21\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuMzIuMTgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=0721c2b08e88aa0b31fe1ddf22787497b78c26af245610b9043607f1670cf4f2\"><p>If you\u2019d like to then turn your photo into a video press [ Make video ] and you will see a video, which you can also upscale.<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NTA1My0zZDIzLTcyYmEtOWZlMC0zZWRkZTllM2UyM2YiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDVhZTE3OGFkODkxMzY1OWYyYjc5OCIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTM5OTMyMn0.HCae6XNE-yNNknAJ-pECwJysxxU17B2sp2TDoZuvun8\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NTA1My0zZDIzLTcyYmEtOWZlMC0zZWRkZTllM2UyM2YiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ1YWUxNzhhZDg5MTM2NTlmMmI3OTgiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.u4EHukHBdgwasBrvgSI4i9kbjRlR-50Mf1STQ95F0iA\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"rka640pbi3l\" data-toc-id=\"rka640pbi3l\"><strong>Step 3: Hover over any photo or video<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Go to your Photo AI gallery and hover over the photo or video you want to upscale.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975034-f395-7880-822d-b237628eb8dd\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTYuNDIuMTAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 16.42.10.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975034-f395-7880-822d-b237628eb8dd\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTYuNDIuMTAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=996638334ad9b1e3cf646978b2f9cdbfc71479dd6469cfcb939bbd71ff6181f4\"><h2 id=\"e526yq1tipo\" data-toc-id=\"e526yq1tipo\"><strong>Step 4: Click [ Upscale ] to upscale it by 2x<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Photo AI will automatically generate a higher-resolution version of your photo or video:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975038-345c-72be-aa5d-5a79de39745c\/b64u-MTc0OTM5NzMzOS0zMDdhZWM3OTM0YTc1Y2YxZjU1YTU5NmNhMGU2MzMxNC0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749397339-307aec7934a75cf1f55a596ca0e63314-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975038-345c-72be-aa5d-5a79de39745c\/b64u-MTc0OTM5NzMzOS0zMDdhZWM3OTM0YTc1Y2YxZjU1YTU5NmNhMGU2MzMxNC0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=2a574ee591f204df157e1c540e5a4f0e333c04582ff2eb206ce627904937de65\"><h2 id=\"oqmsstw2i3w\" data-toc-id=\"oqmsstw2i3w\"><strong>Step 5 (optional): Upscale again to 4x<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">You can upscale an upscaled photo again to get it to 4x super size. We use a different upscale model for the second pass.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975038-d258-7a71-84c1-ca5207e7d726\/b64u-MTc0OTM5NzQxMy1kODA1ZmRjZjc0ZDY1MDNlNDE2ZThhMGQ0ODA5YTIzMS0xLnBuZw.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749397413-d805fdcf74d6503e416e8a0d4809a231-1.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975038-d258-7a71-84c1-ca5207e7d726\/b64u-MTc0OTM5NzQxMy1kODA1ZmRjZjc0ZDY1MDNlNDE2ZThhMGQ0ODA5YTIzMS0xLnBuZw.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=cf671a23c04478d37329632b53d4bc2bd9ba382c460656981a6553b524c7ef4c\"><h2 id=\"ofwbk7poorl\" data-toc-id=\"ofwbk7poorl\">Compare the levels<\/h2><p>If we zoom in at the eyes we can more clearly see the increase in detail for each 2x or 4x upscale pass!<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/0197503d-3153-7761-b196-23010a38d914\/b64u-TmV3IFByb2plY3QgKDEpLndlYnA.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"New Project (1).webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/0197503d-3153-7761-b196-23010a38d914\/b64u-TmV3IFByb2plY3QgKDEpLndlYnA.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=4e3c52b45208a54cf6013045b64c0b8ead4efcc32843e9afd9ea3f23fc5f901f\"><p>Most importantly each upscale is a way higher resolution, making it more suited for broadcast or large-sized print materials. The final pic here is 3072x4096, up from 768\u00d71024!<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975037-e059-7c6d-b843-dbac83dc1a4a\/b64u-MTc0OTMwNjYyNy1iNTE5MzIzZDg3ZDY2NDJlNzJkMGFhN2M1ZmNjNmU4ZC00LndlYnA.webp\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749306627-b519323d87d6642e72d0aa7c5fcc6e8d-4.webp\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/6845ae178ad8913659f2b798\/01975037-e059-7c6d-b843-dbac83dc1a4a\/b64u-MTc0OTMwNjYyNy1iNTE5MzIzZDg3ZDY2NDJlNzJkMGFhN2M1ZmNjNmU4ZC00LndlYnA.webp?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=cbccb6ea8ba0648394123551b14deaf236f1d80f573cc07dd9fb634ec14e7013\"><h2 id=\"y2w886bw5m5\" data-toc-id=\"y2w886bw5m5\">Can I upscale videos too?<\/h2><p>Yes and it works the same. Although you can only do a single 2x pass with [ Upscale ].<\/p><video loading=\"lazy\" controls loop muted data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NTA1My0zZDIzLTcyYmEtOWZlMC0zZWRkZTllM2UyM2YiLCJ0eXBlIjoidmlkZW8tdXJsIiwicmVzb3VyY2VJZCI6IjY4NDVhZTE3OGFkODkxMzY1OWYyYjc5OCIsInJlc291cmNlVHlwZSI6ImFydGljbGUiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsImlhdCI6MTc0OTM5OTMyMn0.HCae6XNE-yNNknAJ-pECwJysxxU17B2sp2TDoZuvun8\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/videos\/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJvYmplY3RLZXkiOiIwMTk3NTA1My0zZDIzLTcyYmEtOWZlMC0zZWRkZTllM2UyM2YiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUyMTQwMDAsInR5cGUiOiJ2aWRlby11cmwiLCJvcmdJZCI6IjY2NGI5MzA1NzRmY2E1YTZhNjVmMzA3YyIsInJlc291cmNlSWQiOiI2ODQ1YWUxNzhhZDg5MTM2NTlmMmI3OTgiLCJyZXNvdXJjZVR5cGUiOiJhcnRpY2xlIn0.u4EHukHBdgwasBrvgSI4i9kbjRlR-50Mf1STQ95F0iA\/manifest.mpd\"><\/video><h2 id=\"827ob2ppd00\" data-toc-id=\"827ob2ppd00\"><strong>Why use Upscale?<\/strong><\/h2><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">Print your AI photos at large sizes without blur<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Make your visuals stand out with extra clarity<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Fix low-res images for better performance in ads<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Use images across more formats and platforms<\/p><\/li><\/ul><h2 id=\"s76fi2xkq14\" data-toc-id=\"s76fi2xkq14\"><strong>Try Upscale now<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\">Your best AI photo and video just got sharper. Use <strong>[ Upscale ]<\/strong> in <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq7\">Photo AI<\/a> to unlock maximum quality \u2014 in one click.<\/p><p><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/how-much-will-my-ai-photos-look-like-me">
							How much will my AI photos look like me?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How much will my AI photos look like me?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Yes. <strong>Photo AI has the highest resemblance\/likeness of any AI apps right now<\/strong>. Simply because we use the highest step count and processing time to both train your AI model and generate photos with it.<\/p><p>Other AI apps cheapen out on processing time to save money on GPU costs and that means it looks kinda like you but not fully.<\/p><p>The resemblance of the photos to you does depend on the quality and variety of the photos you upload. The better and more varied your photos, the more accurately the AI can understand and represent your unique characteristics.<\/p><p>Premium and Ultra plans have the highest resemblance.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/how-long-will-it-take-to-create-my-ai-model">
							How long will it take to create my AI model?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How long will it take to create my AI model?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Premium and Ultra subscribers now have extremely fast training at just 90 seconds.<\/p><p>For lower plans it can take 30 minutes to 2 hours.<\/p><p>The longer we train your model the higher quality you get. Which is why the higher plans are more expensive!<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/how-do-i-get-a-receipt-and-invoice-for-my-payment">
							How do I get a receipt and invoice for my payment?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How do I get a receipt and invoice for my payment?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe\\ UI, sans-serif\">After every payment you get a receipt and invoice emailed to you by Stripe.<\/span><\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/where-is-my-refund">
							Where is my refund?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "Where is my refund?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Please allow up to 3 business days for the card issuer to process the credit and for the funds to appear in your account.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/how-to-change-my-invoice-details-like-name-address-and-tax-id">
							How to change my invoice details like name, address and Tax ID?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to change my invoice details like name, address and Tax ID?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>You can update your invoice details directly from your account:<\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 Log in to <strong>Photo AI<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 Click the <strong>Photo AI logo<\/strong> (top left navigation)<\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 Go to <strong>Billing<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 You\u2019ll be redirected to the <strong>Stripe Customer Portal<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 Under Billing Information, click Update information and update your name, address, and Tax ID<\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 Save your changes \u2014 future invoices will use the updated details<\/p><p class=\"p1\">Notes:<\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 Changes apply to <strong>future invoices only<\/strong> (past invoices can\u2019t be edited due to regulation)<\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 Make sure your Tax ID format matches your country\u2019s requirements<\/p><p class=\"p1\">\u2013 If you don\u2019t see the option, ensure you\u2019re logged into the correct account<\/p><p class=\"p1\">P.S. Hab noch einen sch\u00f6nen Tag noch! Ich wei\u00df, du bist Deutscher oder \u00d6sterreicher. :D<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/change-background-ai">
							How to change background of your photos with AI?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How to change background of your photos with AI?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Want your photo in a cozy caf\u00e9, a mountain landscape, or glowing in sunset light \u2014 without retaking it? With Photo AI\u2019s <strong>Relight<\/strong> feature, you can instantly change the <strong>background<\/strong>, <strong>lighting<\/strong>, and overall <strong>mood<\/strong> of any photo. No Photoshop, no technical skills needed.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fd8-a69e-7fcc-9efe-bed7e2d69b52\/b64u-MTc0OTM4OTI5MS1mYmYwNTQ1YjEzNTM1MDMzZTZiYzA1MDM1ZWIxNmE1MS0xLmpwZw.jpeg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fd8-a69e-7fcc-9efe-bed7e2d69b52\/b64u-MTc0OTM4OTI5MS1mYmYwNTQ1YjEzNTM1MDMzZTZiYzA1MDM1ZWIxNmE1MS0xLmpwZw.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=621efbfa243b2615a0c5611d817d940bce2f1401ae2a3a5d3bba6263d59ef2ec\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749389291-fbf0545b13535033e6bc05035eb16a51-1.jpg\"><h2 id=\"kz0etly2tb5\" data-toc-id=\"kz0etly2tb5\"><strong>What is Relight?<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p3\">Relight lets you modify your photo\u2019s <strong>setting<\/strong> and <strong>light source<\/strong> using AI. It can:<\/p><ul><li><p class=\"p1\">Change a dull studio shot into a beach scene<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Add warm golden-hour light<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Replace plain backgrounds with stunning scenery<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"p1\">Match your image\u2019s vibe to your brand or product<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p class=\"p3\">Your model stays exactly the same \u2014 only the environment and lighting changes.<\/p><h2 id=\"08i3e1ksbmo\" data-toc-id=\"08i3e1ksbmo\"><strong>How to use Relight in Photo AI<\/strong><\/h2><p class=\"p4\">Turning your photo into a short video takes less than a minute. Here\u2019s how:<\/p><ol><li><p>Inside Photo AI, first take some photos of the scene you like. Either write your own prompt or use one of our 100s of photo packs.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fb8-72f6-70e7-8f81-e76ca7d41cff\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuMjUuMjcucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 14.25.27.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fb8-72f6-70e7-8f81-e76ca7d41cff\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuMjUuMjcucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=bd47ad2438c4525b39d73ce324a6e2638bafd8037a54c24a89c0a3aee0ef58b6\"><\/li><li><p>Once you see a photo you like but want to change the background or lighting, hover over it and tap [ Relight ].<\/p><p><br>You\u2019ll see a popup that lets you write a prompt which controls the scene\u2019s location, environment and light:<\/p><p><br>In this case I write: \u201cchange to a minimalist fully marble room that is lit by the sun\u201d<\/p><p><\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fb8-b1de-7be7-bed0-db13b9b7200a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuMjYuMTIucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 14.26.12.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fb8-b1de-7be7-bed0-db13b9b7200a\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuMjYuMTIucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=d6f39ad7d1534d4c835592b60a57f7e990befc9dca72642580207449ef9f4568\"><p><\/p><\/li><li><p>Done! You\u2019ll now see your photo with a new location, setting, background and light:<\/p><p><\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fb9-5e11-7657-89eb-baa39b9b7266\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuMjcuMDkucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 14.27.09.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fb9-5e11-7657-89eb-baa39b9b7266\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuMjcuMDkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=404fe02f734a3206d7a63e0a1c1a3e610fbd026128f364be7c08874672fc900b\"><\/li><\/ol><p>Relight has the limitation that it might reduce the resemblance\/likeness of your photo. In that case, try using [ Remix ] to get resemblance back:<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fba-83a8-7d52-95cd-f14b1fc84a44\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuMjguMjYucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 14.28.26.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fba-83a8-7d52-95cd-f14b1fc84a44\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTQuMjguMjYucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=5851565c4be0ef7ce8e48e7297fe87ca683f6b5c1fbd25438d20041eccd9df61\"><p>As you see the left remixed pic has resemblance back again.<\/p><h2 id=\"fq6s5iippts\" data-toc-id=\"fq6s5iippts\">Upload your own images to change the background of<\/h2><p>With Photo AI you can also upload your own images (like real photos you made) and use [ Relight ] on them<\/p><ol><li><p>First go to [ Import into gallery ] and select your image.<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fd9-1268-7072-a472-037d8644b3fa\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuNDMuNTAucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-07 at 15.43.50.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fd9-1268-7072-a472-037d8644b3fa\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDcgYXQgMTUuNDMuNTAucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=0d673ef79a4f258897a21857fad902b6c2a58b442ced5c588dca2b7bff9b6eb0\"><p><\/p><\/li><li><p>Then once it shows up in the gallery, hover over the image and tap [ Relight ].<\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fd9-14da-75de-99da-4cc074c3a869\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMzQuMDgucG5n.png\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-06 at 21.34.08.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fd9-14da-75de-99da-4cc074c3a869\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDYgYXQgMjEuMzQuMDgucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=133983338deabcfa2fadae1a5cbc6c0478bd9fa6fb27fe7327b1d266ed125b3b\"><\/li><\/ol><p>Just like before, write your prompt \u201cchange to a minimalist fully marble room that is lit by the sun\u201d:<\/p><ol start=\"3\"><li><p>It will then take a minute or so and your photo is done. As you see the face was affected pretty badly in this [ Relight ] (which can happen), let\u2019s fix that with one [ Remix ] pass.<\/p><p><\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fdb-bef2-7e67-a2c0-1ef37f5f0e5e\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTUuMDQuNDMucG5n.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fdb-bef2-7e67-a2c0-1ef37f5f0e5e\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTUuMDQuNDMucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=e40e2d7687c01c693586108e5069a74eaa91a664d767b01991ba2037ce6312bc\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 15.04.43.png\"><\/li><li><p>And here you go, it has its likeness back:<\/p><p><\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fdc-6ec0-7e36-bb7d-de4569e74c40\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTUuMDUuMjkucG5n.png\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fdc-6ec0-7e36-bb7d-de4569e74c40\/b64u-Q2xlYW5TaG90IDIwMjUtMDYtMDggYXQgMTUuMDUuMjkucG5n.png?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=be2fb25b6479af49f793abc5550cb2003ded8ae2545664e5319eaf7fa8c421a4\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"CleanShot 2025-06-08 at 15.05.29.png\"><\/li><li><p>And the final comparison before and after:<br><\/p><img data-width=\"100%\" data-align=\"left\" data-featurebase-content-key=\"664b930574fca5a6a65f307c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fdd-8a37-7f0e-b45f-3d92c18782f5\/b64u-MTc0OTM5MTM4Ni0yMDJhNWYwNDQwN2RiMDg1ZTU4YWZiMWRkYWU5ZGNmYS0xLmpwZw.jpeg\" src=\"https:\/\/664b930574fca5a6a65f307c.featurebase-attachments.com\/c\/article\/68458db02b34d3af3cbf7bd8\/01974fdd-8a37-7f0e-b45f-3d92c18782f5\/b64u-MTc0OTM5MTM4Ni0yMDJhNWYwNDQwN2RiMDg1ZTU4YWZiMWRkYWU5ZGNmYS0xLmpwZw.jpeg?X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260403T100000Z&amp;X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Credential=DO801TYC4FCVNNEKURKM%2F20260403%2Ffra1%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;X-Amz-Signature=5421865979f00c8ae0f61931540e3fab042d60887795aa883544c599cf870b8f\" data-featurebase-content-filename=\"1749391386-202a5f04407db085e58afb1ddae9dcfa-1.jpg\"><\/li><\/ol><p>Try [ Relight ] now on <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer  \" class=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/photoai.com\/?ref=faq7\">Photo AI<\/a>!<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/my-payment-card-is-not-accepted-when-signing-up">
							My payment card is not accepted when signing up						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "My payment card is not accepted when signing up",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>Due to lots of fraud attempts, we've had to increase our payment security. Firstly, disable your VPN or proxy server. Then make sure your name, CVC and postal code match the one on your payment card and of your bank account. Also your card country should be the same as your billing country. And finally make sure you enable 3D Secure or similar authentication on your card with your bank.<\/p><p>We also do not accept customers from the Philippines due to massive and repeated card abuse from there. We\u2019re not planning to change this any time soon.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/i-accidentally-signed-up-for-the-yearly-plan-but-i-want-monthly">
							I accidentally signed up for the yearly plan, but I want monthly						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "I accidentally signed up for the yearly plan, but I want monthly",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>You can get your refund if you haven\u2019t extensively used Photo AI yet, and then sign up again to the right monthly plan.<\/p><p>First get your refund:<\/p><ol><li><p><strong>Get your refund<\/strong><\/p><\/li><\/ol><p>Please login, then tap the top left Photo AI logo, and in the dropdown select [ Request a refund ]. If you\u2019re eligible for a refund, you\u2019ll be able to self-refund on that page.<\/p><p>You're only eligible for a refund if you've not created a model yet and have generated fewer than 20 photos over the lifetime of your account. If you've already used Photo AI to create a model or take photos or videos, we cannot offer a refund as costs incurred for generative AI are extremely high.<\/p><ol start=\"2\"><li><p><strong>Your yearly subscription is now cancelled immediately<\/strong><\/p><\/li><\/ol><ol start=\"2\"><li><p><strong>Change your plan<\/strong><\/p><\/li><\/ol><p>Now login to Photo AI again and you\u2019ll be sent to the pricing table to choose your plan. Make sure you choose the monthly plan this time.<\/p><p>You\u2019ll now have received a refund, cancelled your yearly subscription and signed up to the monthly plan.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
										<h4>
						<a href="/faq/how-do-i-upgrade-or-downgrade-my-plan">
							How do I upgrade or downgrade my plan?						</a>
					</h4>
					<script type="application/ld+json">
						{
							"@context": "https://schema.org",
							"@type": "QAPage",
							"mainEntity": {
								"@type": "Question",
								"name": "Photo AI",
								"text": "How do I upgrade or downgrade my plan?",
								"answerCount": "1",
								"upvoteCount": "1",
								"dateCreated": "2023-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
								"dateModified": "2023-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
								"acceptedAnswer": {
									"@type": "Answer",
									"text": "<p>You can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. <\/p><p>Go to the top left and click the Photo AI logo, when you are logged in and click Billing, you will be redirected to Stripe's billing portal where you can switch plans. <\/p><p>Downgrades will activate at the next billing cycle. Upgrades are instant.<\/p>",
									"upvoteCount": "1",
									"dateCreated": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00",
									"dateModified": "2026-04-03T09:35:27+00:00"
								}
							}
						}
					</script>
								</div>
		</div>
